orces unit that hunts werewolves), and Michael, the werewolf hybrid, work together in an effort to unlock the secrets of their respective bloodlines.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yT1EDKhCzAumcZeBoAxqm0nY2H8.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.575,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:21','834',106,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0401855','David Leitch','Screen Gems','Underworld: Evolution',23,NULL,NULL),(137,'Cowboys & Aliens','2011-07-29','A stranger stumbles into the desert town of Absolution with no memory of his past and a futuristic shackle around his wrist. With the help of mysterious beauty Ella and the iron-fisted Colonel Dolarhyde, he finds himself leading an unlikely posse of cowboys, outlaws, and Apache warriors against a common enemy from beyond this world in an epic showdown for survival.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9uZsGCP4rvOHVGCpMpYq5gNCuNI.jpg','movie',NULL,5,5.597,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:22','49849',119,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0409847','Steven Spielberg','DreamWorks Pictures','Cowboys & Aliens',22,NULL,NULL),(138,'Charlotte\'s Web','2006-12-07','Wilbur the pig is scared of the end of the season, because he knows that come that time, he will end up on the dinner table. He hatches a plan with Charlotte, a spider that lives in his pen, to ensure that this will never happen.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fU0IR5HF8KxQbZijuWKPTrY81Qv.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.199,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-05 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:22','9986',97,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0413895','Gary Winick','Paramount','Charlotte\'s Web',20,NULL,NULL),(139,'Avengers: Infinity War','2018-04-25','As the Avengers and their allies have continued to protect the world from threats too large for any one hero to handle, a new danger has emerged from the cosmic shadows: Thanos. A despot of intergalactic infamy, his goal is to collect all six Infinity Stones, artifacts of unimaginable power, and use them to inflict his twisted will on all of reality. Everything the Avengers have fought for has led up to this moment - the fate of Earth and existence itself has never been more uncertain.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7WsyChQLEftFiDOVTGkv3hFpyyt.jpg','movie',NULL,6,8.251,NULL,NULL,'2018-08-29 00:00:00','2024-11-11 20:40:17','299536',149,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4154756','Anthony Russo','Marvel Studios','Avengers: Infinity War',22,NULL,NULL),(140,'Surf\'s Up','2007-06-08','A young surfer enters his first contest, hoping a win will earn him respect. But an encounter with a laid-back local forces him to rethink his values.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tTDsCVlDA8QR4Dc6t6nERfwl5z.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.394,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:23','9408',85,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0423294','Chris Buck','Columbia Pictures','Surf\'s Up',21,NULL,NULL),(141,'The Witch','2015-01-27','In 1630, a farmer relocates his family to a remote plot of land on the edge of a forest where strange, unsettling things happen. With suspicion and paranoia mounting, each family member\'s faith, loyalty and love are tested in shocking ways.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zap5hpFCWSvdWSuPGAQyjUv2wAC.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.936,NULL,NULL,'2019-08-12 00:00:00','2024-02-13 00:33:22','310131',92,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4263482','Chris Columbus','Very Special Projects','The Witch',23,NULL,3),(142,'The Ant Bully','2006-07-28','Fed up with being targeted by the neighborhood bully, 10-year-old Lucas Nickle vents his frustrations on the anthill in his front yard ... until the insects shrink him to the size of a bug with a magic elixir. Convicted of \"crimes against the colony,\" Lucas can only regain his freedom by living with the ants and learning their ways.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oFuqX0inTvbA1XAFv2x3CQnI65m.jpg','movie',NULL,5,5.7,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:24','9906',88,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0429589','Keith Alcorn','DNA Productions','The Ant Bully',21,NULL,NULL),(143,'Pokémon: Destiny Deoxys','2004-07-22','Deoxys, a Pokémon from outer space, terrorizes the high-tech city Ash Ketchum and his friends are visiting.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uEeLCGLIXH1ElS53hyUQInJB0Ub.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.598,NULL,NULL,'2018-02-20 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:24','34065',98,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0435286','Kunihiko Yuyama','Pikachu Project','Pokémon: Destiny Deoxys',21,NULL,NULL),(144,'Toy Story 3','2010-06-16','Woody, Buzz, and the rest of Andy\'s toys haven\'t been played with in years. With Andy about to go to college, the gang find themselves accidentally left at a nefarious day care center. The toys must band together to escape and return home to Andy.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/AbbXspMOwdvwWZgVN0nabZq03Ec.jpg','movie',NULL,5,7.792,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:24','10193',103,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0435761','Lee Unkrich','Pixar','Toy Story 3',20,NULL,NULL),(145,'G-Force','2009-07-24','A team of trained secret agent animals, guinea pigs Darwin, Hurley, Juarez, Blaster, mole Speckles, and fly Mooch takes on a mission for the US government to stop evil Leonard Saber, who plans to destroy the world with household appliances. But the government shuts them down and they are sentenced to a pet shop. Can they escape to defeat the villain and save the world?','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jpjG88kTrK7mHnRx4cpLHh8YZwr.jpg','movie',NULL,5,5.442,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:24','19585',88,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0436339','Trudy Ramirez','Walt Disney Pictures','G-Force',21,NULL,NULL),(146,'Horton Hears a Who!','2008-03-03','The classic and beloved story from Dr. Seuss is now a CG animated film from 20th Century Fox Animation, the makers of the Ice Age films. An imaginative elephant named Horton (Jim Carrey) hears a faint cry for help coming from a tiny speck of dust floating through the air. Horton suspects there may be life on that speck and despite a surrounding community, which thinks he has lost his mind, he is determined to save the tiny particle! Jim Carrey and Steve Carell lead an all-star cast in bringing this wonderful family picture to life!','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6k47Z3A5zI2rxubTMwiLyIqQLLr.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.5,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:25','12222',86,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0451079','Steve Martino','Blue Sky Studios','Horton Hears a Who!',20,NULL,NULL),(147,'Garfield: A Tail of Two Kitties','2006-06-15','Jon and Garfield visit the United Kingdom, where a case of mistaken cat identity finds Garfield ruling over a castle. His reign is soon jeopardized by the nefarious Lord Dargis, who has designs on the estate.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/osfMaHucgLtHtsMa6TQLTooE3G7.jpg','movie',NULL,5,5.6,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:25','9513',78,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0455499','Tim Hill','20th Century Fox','Garfield: A Tail of Two Kitties',21,NULL,NULL),(149,'Prince of Persia: The Sands of Time','2010-05-19','A rogue prince reluctantly joins forces with a mysterious princess and together, they race against dark forces to safeguard an ancient dagger capable of releasing the Sands of Time – gift from the gods that can reverse time and allow its possessor to rule the world.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/siNGMLdOUNYLEGtlsnmQcpO2XZX.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.27,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:27','9543',116,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0473075','Mike Newell','Walt Disney Pictures','Prince of Persia: The Sands of Time',22,NULL,NULL),(150,'The Sucker','1965-03-24','In this Frenco-Italian gangster parody, a shop keeper on his way to an Italian holiday suffers a crash which totals his car. The culprit can only compensate his ruined trip by driving an American friends car from Napels to Bordeaux, but as it happens to be filled with such contraband as stolen money, jewelry and drugs, the involuntary and unwitting companions in crime soon attract all but recreational attention from the \"milieu\".','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xkCGWJ0GYx3nK2PoFZdpl6L49q1.jpg','movie',NULL,5,7.361,NULL,NULL,'2018-02-22 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:29','25866',111,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0057967',NULL,'Les Films Corona','The Sucker',22,NULL,NULL),(151,'Doctor Dolittle','1998-06-26','A successful physician and devoted family man, John Dolittle seems to have the world by the tail, until a long suppressed talent he possessed as a child, the ability to communicate with animals is suddenly reawakened with a vengeance! Now every creature within squawking distance wants the good doctor\'s advice, unleashing an outrageous chain of events that turns his world upside down!','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tLrchGMIkdo1KamQJA6fwvDQEy0.jpg','movie',NULL,5,5.683,NULL,NULL,'2020-10-31 01:07:29','2024-01-25 23:41:29','3050',85,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0118998','Betty Thomas','20th Century Fox','Doctor Dolittle',22,NULL,NULL),(152,'World War Z','2013-06-20','Life for former United Nations investigator Gerry Lane and his family seems content. Suddenly, the world is plagued by a mysterious infection turning whole human populations into rampaging mindless zombies. After barely escaping the chaos, Lane is persuaded to go on a mission to investigate this disease. What follows is a perilous trek around the world where Lane must brave horrific dangers and long odds to find answers before human civilization falls.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1SWBSYJsnyhdNRfLI1T6RsCxAQ4.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.811,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:34','72190',116,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0816711','Marc Forster','GK Films','World War Z',22,NULL,NULL),(153,'Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs','2009-09-17','Inventor Flint Lockwood creates a machine that makes clouds rain food, enabling the down-and-out citizens of Chewandswallow to feed themselves. But when the falling food reaches gargantuan proportions, Flint must scramble to avert disaster. Can he regain control of the machine and put an end to the wild weather before the town is destroyed?','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qhOhIKf7QEyQ5dMrRUqs5eTX1Oq.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.609,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:35','22794',90,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0844471','Will Gluck','Sony Pictures Animation','Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs',21,NULL,NULL),(154,'Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom','1984-05-23','After arriving in India, Indiana Jones is asked by a desperate village to find a mystical stone. He agrees – and stumbles upon a secret cult plotting a terrible plan in the catacombs of an ancient palace.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t7Pv44sBcxhc47kNNDDafNAgr7Y.jpg','movie',NULL,5,7.297,NULL,NULL,'2021-05-02 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:36','87',118,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0087469','George Lucas','Paramount','Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom',21,NULL,NULL),(155,'The Black Cauldron','1985-07-24','Taran is an assistant pigkeeper with boyish dreams of becoming a great warrior. However, he has to put the daydreaming aside when his charge, an oracular pig named Hen Wen, is kidnapped by an evil lord known as the Horned King. The villain hopes Hen will show him the way to The Black Cauldron, which has the power to create a giant army of unstoppable soldiers.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/act8vtlXVEizdsUf9FcKbzSERew.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.433,NULL,NULL,'2018-01-06 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:37','10957',80,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0088814','Chris Buck','Silver Screen Partners II','The Black Cauldron',21,NULL,NULL),(156,'Monsters vs Aliens','2009-03-19','When Susan Murphy is unwittingly clobbered by a meteor full of outer space gunk on her wedding day, she mysteriously grows to 49-feet-11-inches. The military jumps into action and captures Susan, secreting her away to a covert government compound. She is renamed Ginormica and placed in confinement with a ragtag group of Monsters...','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hpHarddVj34j53T7NsoUGdKj4mP.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.2,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:38','15512',94,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0892782','Rob Letterman','DreamWorks Animation','Monsters vs Aliens',21,NULL,NULL),(157,'Knives Out','2019-11-27','When renowned crime novelist Harlan Thrombey is found dead at his estate just after his 85th birthday, the inquisitive and debonair Detective Benoit Blanc is mysteriously enlisted to investigate. From Harlan\'s dysfunctional family to his devoted staff, Blanc sifts through a web of red herrings and self-serving lies to uncover the truth behind Harlan\'s untimely death.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pThyQovXQrw2m0s9x82twj48Jq4.jpg','movie',NULL,5,7.845,NULL,NULL,'2020-02-29 00:00:00','2025-02-10 23:50:49','546554',131,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt8946378','Rian Johnson','Lionsgate','Knives Out',22,NULL,NULL),(158,'The Kid Detective','2020-10-16','A once-celebrated kid detective, now 31, continues to solve the same trivial mysteries between hangovers and bouts of self-pity. Until a naive client brings him his first \'adult\' case, to find out who brutally murdered her boyfriend.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2WrT8AZUcDicvf5m8KVgspQEHK3.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.566,NULL,NULL,'2021-04-08 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:38','720755',99,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt8980602','Sydney Kondruss','Woods Entertainment','The Kid Detective',23,NULL,NULL),(159,'Little Shop of Horrors','1986-12-19','Seymour Krelborn is a nerdy orphan working at Mushnik\'s, a flower shop in urban Skid Row. He harbors a crush on fellow co-worker Audrey Fulquard, and is berated by Mr. Mushnik daily. One day Seymour finds a very mysterious unidentified plant which he calls Audrey II. The plant seems to have a craving for blood and soon begins to sing for his supper.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iKkbN17OmFosaW6asCNZTTsyvpu.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.899,NULL,NULL,'2021-04-10 00:00:00','2025-03-16 06:54:47','10776',94,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0091419','Bran Ferren','Geffen Pictures','Little Shop of Horrors',22,NULL,NULL),(160,'Spaceballs','1987-06-24','When the nefarious Dark Helmet hatches a plan to snatch Princess Vespa and steal her planet\'s air, space-bum-for-hire Lone Starr and his clueless sidekick fly to the rescue. Along the way, they meet Yogurt, who puts Lone Starr wise to the power of \"The Schwartz.\" Can he master it in time to save the day?','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/o624HTt93iIJIc1Sg5hNkDTnk5l.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.84,NULL,NULL,'2017-10-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:39','957',96,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0094012',NULL,'Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer','Spaceballs',21,NULL,NULL),(161,'Source Code','2011-03-30','When decorated soldier Captain Colter Stevens wakes up in the body of an unknown man, he discovers he\'s part of a mission to find the bomber of a Chicago commuter train.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/faCR2lavXBKeCS6N7STIMDLMCDL.jpg','movie',NULL,5,7.3,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:39','45612',94,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0945513','Duncan Jones','The Mark Gordon Company','Source Code',22,NULL,NULL),(162,'The Sorcerer\'s Apprentice','2010-07-13','Balthazar Blake is a master sorcerer in modern-day Manhattan trying to defend the city from his arch-nemesis, Maxim Horvath. Balthazar can\'t do it alone, so he recruits Dave Stutler, a seemingly average guy who demonstrates hidden potential, as his reluctant protégé. The sorcerer gives his unwilling accomplice a crash course in the art and science of magic, and together, these unlikely partners work to stop the forces of darkness.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/b5pIUsGll0418NyfNA5eYCI9aoK.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.107,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:40','27022',