vertently brings turmoil to the kingdom. In an attempt to set things right, Mérida seeks out an eccentric old Wise Woman and is granted an ill-fated wish. Also figuring into Mérida’s quest — and serving as comic relief — are the kingdom’s three lords: the enormous Lord MacGuffin, the surly Lord Macintosh, and the disagreeable Lord Dingwall.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1XAuDtMWpL0sYSFK0R6EZate2Ux.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.015,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:53','62177',93,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1217209','Robert Anderson','Walt Disney Pictures','Brave',21,NULL,NULL),(191,'Pokémon: The Rise of Darkrai','2007-07-14','Ash and friends (this time accompanied by newcomer Dawn) arrive at an idyllic village on their way to their next Pokemon contest, where chaos will soon erupt with the prophecy of two Pokemon Gods (Dialga and Palkia) and the arrival of a mysterious, seemingly deadly Pokemon named Darkrai, which has the power to distort space and time.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9TcvVXElhZ1e4J3n6JUIDKpZiTE.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.87,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:53','25961',90,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1226251','Kunihiko Yuyama','Pikachu Project','Pokémon: The Rise of Darkrai',20,NULL,NULL),(192,'Iron Man 2','2010-04-28','With the world now aware of his dual life as the armored superhero Iron Man, billionaire inventor Tony Stark faces pressure from the government, the press and the public to share his technology with the military. Unwilling to let go of his invention, Stark, with Pepper Potts and James \'Rhodey\' Rhodes at his side, must forge new alliances – and confront powerful enemies.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6WBeq4fCfn7AN0o21W9qNcRF2l9.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.837,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:53','10138',124,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1228705','Chad Stahelski','Marvel Studios','Iron Man 2',22,NULL,NULL),(193,'Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol','2011-12-07','Ethan Hunt and his team are racing against time to track down a dangerous terrorist named Hendricks, who has gained access to Russian nuclear launch codes and is planning a strike on the United States. An attempt to stop him ends in an explosion causing severe destruction to the Kremlin and the IMF to be implicated in the bombing, forcing the President to disavow them. No longer being aided by the government, Ethan and his team chase Hendricks around the globe, although they might still be too late to stop a disaster.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/psiWp3VTjznfokmGQG9uqiiknQQ.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.077,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:53','56292',133,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1229238','J.J. Abrams','Paramount','Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol',22,NULL,NULL),(194,'Cube','1997-09-09','A group of strangers find themselves trapped in a maze-like prison. It soon becomes clear that each of them possesses the peculiar skills necessary to escape, if they don\'t wind up dead first.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lBdCYZIeSF3ub3w5lhbTB0n32Fe.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.8,NULL,NULL,'2020-01-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:54','431',90,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0123755','Vincenzo Natali','Cube Libre','Cube',23,NULL,NULL),(195,'Kick-Ass','2010-03-22','Dave Lizewski is an unnoticed high school student and comic book fan who one day decides to become a super-hero, even though he has no powers, training or meaningful reason to do so.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8citjdBmjddZjlPsAHEyCKwGVvD.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.121,NULL,NULL,'2016-08-28 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:54','23483',117,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1250777','Annie Penn','Marv','Kick-Ass',23,NULL,NULL),(196,'The Cabin in the Woods','2012-04-12','Five friends go for a break at a remote cabin, where they get more than they bargained for, discovering the truth behind the cabin in the woods.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kjDXrK3ReIwuDrpWElI5OQkKYTA.jpg','m