rX.jpg','movie',NULL,6,5.884,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:58','1995',100,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0146316','Simon West','Paramount','Lara Croft: Tomb Raider',22,NULL,NULL),(207,'The Lego Movie','2014-02-06','An ordinary Lego mini-figure, mistakenly thought to be the extraordinary MasterBuilder, is recruited to join a quest to stop an evil Lego tyrant from conquering the universe.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9klB7qKC9aCeGyyM4uU5hSA6xDV.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.42,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:58','137106',100,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1490017','Chris McKay','Village Roadshow Pictures','The Lego Movie',21,NULL,NULL),(208,'The King\'s Speech','2010-11-26','The King\'s Speech tells the story of the man who became King George VI, the father of Queen Elizabeth II. After his brother abdicates, George (\'Bertie\') reluctantly assumes the throne. Plagued by a dreaded stutter and considered unfit to be king, Bertie engages the help of an unorthodox speech therapist named Lionel Logue. Through a set of unexpected techniques, and as a result of an unlikely friendship, Bertie is able to find his voice and boldly lead the country into war.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uQ538BfYLDJh3GXlzRZLo0j7PFj.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.742,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:59','45269',118,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1504320','Chris Stoaling','The Weinstein Company','The King\'s Speech',23,NULL,NULL),(209,'Mad God','2022-06-16','A figure known as \"The Assassin\" descends from the heavens into a nightmarish pit full of monsters, titans, and cruelty.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sEULzxEZvrJvhz91wKxpbih25Sk.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.854,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-06 00:00:00','2025-07-02 16:40:19','846867',84,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt15090124','Ri Crawford','Tippett Studio','Mad God',23,NULL,3),(210,'Nothing to Declare','2010-12-20','During the elimination of the Belgian/French border in the 90s, a Belgian customs officer is forced to team up with one of his French counterparts.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vqJmmfVavVX9F9De3LQLDlGPc6D.jpg','movie',NULL,6,5.856,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-22 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:59','52077',108,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1528313',NULL,'SCOPE Invest','Nothing to Declare',22,NULL,NULL),(211,'Elysium','2013-08-07','In the year 2159, two classes of people exist: the very wealthy who live on a pristine man-made space station called Elysium, and the rest, who live on an overpopulated, ruined Earth. Secretary Rhodes, a hard line government ofﬁcial, will stop at nothing to enforce anti-immigration laws and preserve the luxurious lifestyle of the citizens of Elysium. That doesn’t stop the people of Earth from trying to get in, by any means they can. When unlucky Max is backed into a corner, he agrees to take on a daunting mission that, if successful, will not only save his life, but could bring equality to these polarized worlds.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aRjuJuPXHtVs6YegfeeQWXGRs1E.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.504,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:59','68724',109,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1535108','Neill Blomkamp','TriStar Pictures','Elysium',23,NULL,NULL),(212,'Romantics Anonymous','2010-12-22','What happens when a man and a woman share a common passion? They fall in love. And this is what happens to Jean-René, the boss of a small chocolate factory, and Angélique, a gifted chocolate maker he has just hired. What occurs when a highly emotional man meets a highly emotional woman? They fall in love, and this is what occurs to Jean-René and Angélique who share the same handicap. But being pathologically timid does not make things easy for them. So whether they will manage to get together, join their solitudes and live happily ever after is a guessing matter.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hXL5TgqgFF8159dez0o8EK11ve3.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.495,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:46:59','51991',80,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1565958','Jean-Pierre Améris','Pan-Européenne','Romantics Anonymous',20,NULL,NULL),(213,'The Grey','2012-01-26','Following a grueling five-week shift at an Alaskan oil refinery, workers led by sharpshooter John Ottway, are flying home for a much-needed vacation. But a brutal storm causes their plane to crash in the frozen wilderness, and only eight men, including Ottway, survive. As they trek southward toward civilization and safety, Ottway and his companions must battle mortal injuries, the icy elements, and a pack of hungry wolves.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a0Vt3wx8ciKmPt4iXPx9sH4HBVU.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.6,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:00','75174',117,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1601913','Ridley Scott','Open Road Films','The Grey',23,NULL,NULL),(214,'Edge of Tomorrow','2014-05-27','Major Bill Cage is an officer who has never seen a day of combat when he is unceremoniously demoted and dropped into combat. Cage is killed within minutes, managing to take an alpha alien down with him. He awakens back at the beginning of the same day and is forced to fight and die again... and again - as physical contact with the alien has thrown him into a time loop.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xjw5trHV7Mwo61P0kCTy8paEkgO.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.614,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:00','137113',114,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1631867','Doug Liman','RatPac Entertainment','Edge of Tomorrow',22,NULL,NULL),(215,'Johnny English Reborn','2011-09-15','The most prominent heads of state in the world begin gathering for a conference that could have a major impact on global politics. When MI-7 receives word that the Chinese premier has become the target of some high-powered killers, it falls on Johnny English to save the day. Armed with the latest high-tech weaponry and gadgets that would make even James Bond jealous, the once-disgraced agent uncovers evidence of a massive conspiracy involving some of the world\'s most powerful organisations, and vows to redeem his tarnished reputation by stopping the killers before they can strike.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1T6qnlTVkrGr0mpgZbpSwVU5FWW.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.228,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:01','58233',101,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1634122','Oliver Parker','Working Title Films','Johnny English Reborn',21,NULL,NULL),(216,'Ted','2012-06-29','John Bennett, a man whose childhood wish of bringing his teddy bear to life came true, now must decide between keeping the relationship with the bear or his girlfriend, Lori.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1QVZXQQHCEIj8lyUhdBYd2qOYtq.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.415,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:01','72105',107,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1637725','Eric Heffron','Universal Pictures','Ted',23,NULL,NULL),(217,'Super 8','2011-06-08','In 1979 Ohio, several youngsters are making a zombie movie with a Super-8 camera. In the midst of filming, the friends witness a horrifying train derailment and are lucky to escape with their lives. They soon discover that the catastrophe was no accident, as a series of unexplained events and disappearances soon follows. Deputy Jackson Lamb, the father of one of the kids, searches for the terrifying truth behind the crash.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sytFL6ALMAesKZoarlp7bIDKnns.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.762,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:01','37686',112,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1650062','Steven Spielberg','Paramount','Super 8',22,NULL,NULL),(218,'Sinbad: Legend of the Seven Seas','2003-07-02','The sailor of legend is framed by the goddess Eris for the theft of the Book of Peace, and must travel to her realm at the end of the world to retrieve it and save the life of his childhood friend Prince Proteus.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yiW2L1fDiBT7AeWXrykhTNtPrr8.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.948,NULL,NULL,'2