/hQQCdZrsHtZyR6NbKH2YyCqd2fR.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.436,NULL,NULL,'2019-01-15 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:09','161',116,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0240772','Steven Soderbergh','Warner Bros. Pictures','Ocean\'s Eleven',22,NULL,NULL),(235,'The Bourne Identity','2002-06-14','Wounded to the brink of death and suffering from amnesia, Jason Bourne is rescued at sea by a fisherman. With nothing to go on but a Swiss bank account number, he starts to reconstruct his life, but finds that many people he encounters want him dead. However, Bourne realizes that he has the combat and mental skills of a world-class spy—but who does he work for?','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aP8swke3gmowbkfZ6lmNidu0y9p.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.467,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:11','2501',119,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0258463','Frank Marshall','Universal Pictures','The Bourne Identity',22,NULL,NULL),(236,'Ted 2','2015-06-25','Newlywed couple Ted and Tami-Lynn want to have a baby, but in order to qualify to be a parent, Ted will have to prove he\'s a person in a court of law.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qMOt0uy1x49OBW0jzodgRM9waW0.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.294,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:11','214756',115,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2637276','Eric Heffron','Smart Entertainment','Ted 2',23,NULL,NULL),(237,'Star Trek Beyond','2016-07-07','The USS Enterprise crew explores the furthest reaches of uncharted space, where they encounter a mysterious new enemy who puts them and everything the Federation stands for to the test.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yOnd3XQIg7JBmu0UuBjZyLdsxQD.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.783,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:11','188927',122,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2660888','J.J. Abrams','Skydance Media','Star Trek Beyond',22,NULL,NULL),(238,'Scooby-Doo','2002-06-14','When the Mystery Inc. gang is invited to Spooky Island, a popular amusement park, they soon discover that the attractions aren\'t the only things that are spooky. Strange things are happening, and it\'s up to Scooby, Shaggy, Fred, Daphne, and Velma to uncover the truth behind the mysterious happenings.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mTAiBJGg8mqEfnYHHbi37ZoRSZm.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.062,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-11-01 20:36:04','9637',88,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0267913','William Hanna','Mosaic Media Group','Scooby-Doo',21,NULL,NULL),(239,'Ice Age','2002-03-10','With the impending ice age almost upon them, a mismatched trio of prehistoric critters – Manny the woolly mammoth, Diego the saber-toothed tiger and Sid the giant sloth – find an orphaned infant and decide to return it to its human parents. Along the way, the unlikely allies become friends but, when enemies attack, their quest takes on far nobler aims.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gLhHHZUzeseRXShoDyC4VqLgsNv.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.354,NULL,NULL,'2019-08-17 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:11','425',81,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0268380','David Silverman','20th Century Fox Animation','Ice Age',21,NULL,NULL),(240,'Spy Kids 2: The Island of Lost Dreams','2002-08-07','Exploring the further adventures of Carmen and Juni Cortez, who have now joined the family spy business as Level 2 OSS agents. Their new mission is to save the world from a mad scientist living on a volcanic island populated by an imaginative menagerie of creatures. On this bizarre island, none of the Cortez\'s gadgets work and they must rely on their wits--and each other--to survive and save the day.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/z8pfWCk6SlxxDLXXQdUHdxF5dwJ.jpg','movie',NULL,6,5.608,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:12','9488',100,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0287717','Robert Rodriguez','Dimension Films','Spy Kids 2: The Island of Lost Dreams',21,NULL,NULL),(241,'Soul','2020-12-25','Joe Gardner is a middle school teacher with a love for jazz music. After a successful audition at the 