s','2006-06-08','Lightning McQueen, a hotshot rookie race car driven to succeed, discovers that life is about the journey, not the finish line, when he finds himself unexpectedly detoured in the sleepy Route 66 town of Radiator Springs. On route across the country to the big Piston Cup Championship in California to compete against two seasoned pros, McQueen gets to know the town\'s offbeat characters.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/abW5AzHDaIK1n9C36VdAeOwORRA.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.949,NULL,NULL,'2016-08-28 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:14','920',117,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0317219','Lee Unkrich','Pixar','Cars',20,NULL,NULL),(245,'Looney Tunes: Back in Action','2003-11-14','Fed up with all the attention going to Bugs Bunny, Daffy Duck quits Hollywood, teams up with recently-fired stuntman Damien Drake Jr. and embarks on a round-the-world adventure, along with Bugs and The VP of Warner Bros. Their mission? Find Damien\'s father, and the missing blue diamond... and stay one step ahead of The Acme Corp., who wants the diamond for their own purposes.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/q0kntpdsHA0QdYjpQdNBqrVTdQq.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.375,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-06-02 21:14:42','10715',93,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0318155','Joe Dante','Warner Bros. Animation','Looney Tunes: Back in Action',21,NULL,NULL),(246,'The Day After Tomorrow','2004-05-26','After years of increases in the greenhouse effect, havoc is wreaked globally in the form of catastrophic hurricanes, tornadoes, tidal waves, floods and the beginning of a new Ice Age. Paleoclimatologist Jack Hall tries to warn the world while also shepherding to safety his son, trapped in New York after the city is overwhelmed by the start of the new big freeze.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Wr4HeYQRvwVCxzOV5TmGE7UkXq.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.5,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:14','435',124,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0319262','Roland Emmerich','20th Century Fox','The Day After Tomorrow',22,NULL,NULL),(247,'Coraline','2009-02-05','A young girl discovers an idealized parallel universe behind a secret door in her new home, unaware that it contains a sinister secret.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4jeFXQYytChdZYE9JYO7Un87IlW.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.867,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-17 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:14','14836',100,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0327597','Henry Selick','Laika','Coraline',21,NULL,NULL),(248,'Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire','2005-11-16','When Harry Potter\'s name emerges from the Goblet of Fire, he becomes a competitor in a grueling battle for glory among three wizarding schools—the Triwizard Tournament. But since Harry never submitted his name for the Tournament, who did? Now Harry must confront a deadly dragon, fierce water demons and an enchanted maze only to find himself in the cruel grasp of He Who Must Not Be Named.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fECBtHlr0RB3foNHDiCBXeg9Bv9.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.815,NULL,NULL,'2018-04-30 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:15','674',157,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0330373','Mike Newell','Warner Bros. Pictures','Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire',22,NULL,NULL),(249,'Scooby-Doo 2: Monsters Unleashed','2004-03-24','After solving their last mystery at Spooky Island, the Mystery Inc. gang is back in Coolsville, where they are being honored with their very own exhibit at the Coolsonian Criminology Museum. However, when a masked villain steals costumes of classic monsters on display and brings them to life, the gang must come out of retirement to solve the case.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5BrXCJrs22bR5KR6mLHluYo6y4m.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.036,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-11-01 20:35:56','11024',93,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0331632','Anne Fletcher','Mosaic Media Group','Scooby-Doo 2: Monsters Unleashed',21,NULL,NULL),(250,'The Polar Express','2004-11-10','When a doubting young boy takes an extraordinary train ride to the