ut heart and save the day? Romance beckons as well, and a villain lurks.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dR7CzIobFZZgxmO9YxYqBCHU4Pr.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.382,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-12-22 19:45:29','9992',94,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0344854','Luc Besson','Canal+','Arthur and the Invisibles',21,NULL,NULL),(254,'The Disaster Artist','2017-03-12','An aspiring actor in Hollywood meets an enigmatic stranger by the name of Tommy Wiseau, the meeting leads the actor down a path nobody could have predicted; creating the worst movie ever made.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jj84nF5vYRD0HUTowBKcrKk8hZP.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.11,NULL,NULL,'2019-08-17 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:17','371638',104,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3521126','Jonathan Watson','New Line Cinema','The Disaster Artist',23,NULL,NULL),(255,'Captain Fantastic','2016-07-08','A father living in the forests of the Pacific Northwest with his six young kids tries to assimilate back into society.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2sFME73GaD8UsUxPUKe60cPdLif.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.914,NULL,NULL,'2019-08-17 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:17','334533',118,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3553976','Andy Spletzer','Electric City Entertainment','Captain Fantastic',23,NULL,NULL),(256,'Incredibles 2','2018-06-14','Elastigirl springs into action to save the day, while Mr. Incredible faces his greatest challenge yet – taking care of the problems of his three children.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9lFKBtaVIhP7E2Pk0IY1CwTKTMZ.jpg','movie',NULL,5,7.476,NULL,NULL,'2018-07-23 00:00:00','2024-02-20 23:59:19','260513',118,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3606756','Gregg Olsson','Walt Disney Pictures','Incredibles 2',21,NULL,NULL),(257,'Son of the Mask','2005-02-18','Tim Avery, an aspiring cartoonist, finds himself in a predicament when his dog stumbles upon the mask of Loki. Then after conceiving an infant son \"born of the mask\", he discovers just how looney child raising 