 Sacrifice','2015-09-16','American chess champion Bobby Fischer prepares for a legendary match-up against Russian Boris Spassky.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lw6oQ70aLS2thMyUn0CPSYiUiau.jpg','movie',NULL,7,6.76,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:00','245698',115,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1596345','Edward Zwick','Gail Katz Productions','Pawn Sacrifice',22,NULL,NULL),(359,'The Big Short','2015-12-11','The men who made millions from a global economic meltdown.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/isuQWbJPbjybBEWdcCaBUPmU0XO.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.349,NULL,NULL,'2019-03-05 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:00','318846',131,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1596363','Adam McKay','Paramount','The Big Short',23,NULL,NULL),(360,'Sausage Party','2016-07-11','Hot dog Frank leads a group of supermarket products on a quest to discover the truth about their existence and what really happens when they become chosen to leave the grocery store.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vNgdPJQ5CI60oEiiHLKRNrsDhMy.jpg','movie',NULL,5,5.745,NULL,NULL,'2023-04-18 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:02','223702',89,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1700841','Mark Osborne','Columbia Pictures','Sausage Party',23,NULL,NULL),(361,'Top Gun: Maverick','2022-05-24','After more than thirty years of service as one of the Navy’s top aviators, and dodging the advancement in rank that would ground him, Pete “Maverick” Mitchell finds himself training a detachment of TOP GUN graduates for a specialized mission the likes of which no living pilot has ever seen.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/62HCnUTziyWcpDaBO2i1DX17ljH.jpg','movie',NULL,8,8.2,NULL,NULL,'2022-06-25 00:00:00','2024-02-03 00:38:46','361743',131,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1745960','Tony Scott','Skydance Media','Top Gun: Maverick',22,NULL,NULL),(362,'Wreck-It Ralph','2012-11-01','Wreck-It Ralph is the 9-foot-tall, 643-pound villain of an arcade video game named Fix-It Felix Jr., in which the game\'s titular hero fixes buildings that Ralph destroys. Wanting to prove he can be a good guy and not just a villain, Ralph escapes his game and lands in Hero\'s Duty, a first-person shooter where he helps the game\'s hero battle against alien invaders. He later enters Sugar Rush, a kart racing game set on tracks made of candies, cookies and other sweets. There, Ralph meets Vanellope von Schweetz who has learned that her game is faced with a dire threat that could affect the entire arcade, and one that Ralph may have inadvertently started.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zWoIgZ7mgmPkaZjG0102BSKFIqQ.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.333,NULL,NULL,'2017-08-24 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:03','82690',101,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1772341','Bruce W. Smith','Walt Disney Animation Studios','Wreck-It Ralph',21,NULL,NULL),(363,'Requiem for a Dream','2000-10-06','The hopes and dreams of four ambitious people are shattered when their drug addictions begin spiraling out of control. A look into addiction and how it overcomes the mind and body.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nOd6vjEmzCT0k4VYqsA2hwyi87C.jpg','movie',NULL,7,8.023,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-12 00:00:00','2024-02-12 23:22:06','641',102,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0180093','Darren Aronofsky','Artisan Entertainment','Requiem for a Dream',24,NULL,3),(364,'Minority Report','2002-06-20','John Anderton is a top \'Precrime\' cop in the late-21st century, when technology can predict crimes before they\'re committed. But Anderton becomes the quarry when another investigator targets him for a murder charge.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ccqpHq5tk5W4ymbSbuoy4uYOxFI.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.343,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:03','180',145,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0181689','Steven Spielberg','Digital Image Associates','Minority Report',22,NULL,NULL),(365,'Deepwater Horizon','2016-09-28','A story set on the offshore drilling rig Deepwater Horizon, which exploded during April 2010 and created the