 over the kingdom. She\'s accompanied by ice delivery man Kristoff, his reindeer Sven, and snowman Olaf. On an adventure where she will find out what friendship, courage, family, and true love really means.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kgwjIb2JDHRhNk13lmSxiClFjVk.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.246,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:07','109445',102,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2294629','Chris Buck','Walt Disney Pictures','Frozen',21,NULL,NULL),(373,'The Intern','2015-09-23','70-year-old widower Ben Whittaker has discovered that retirement isn\'t all it\'s cracked up to be. Seizing an opportunity to get back in the game, he becomes a senior intern at an online fashion site, founded and run by Jules Ostin.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9UoAC9tu8kIyRy8AcJnGhnH0gOH.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.203,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:08','257211',121,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2361509','Jeffrey Wetzel','Warner Bros. Pictures','The Intern',22,NULL,NULL),(374,'Coco','2017-10-27','Despite his family’s baffling generations-old ban on music, Miguel dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol, Ernesto de la Cruz. Desperate to prove his talent, Miguel finds himself in the stunning and colorful Land of the Dead following a mysterious chain of events. Along the way, he meets charming trickster Hector, and together, they set off on an extraordinary journey to unlock the real story behind Miguel\'s family history.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gGEsBPAijhVUFoiNpgZXqRVWJt2.jpg','movie',NULL,7,8.215,NULL,NULL,'2021-03-14 00:00:00','2024-11-11 20:41:20','354912',105,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2380307','Lee Unkrich','Pixar','Coco',21,NULL,NULL),(375,'Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation','2015-07-23','Ethan and team take on their most impossible mission yet—eradicating \'The Syndicate\', an International and highly-skilled rogue organization committed to destroying the IMF.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sGvcW