out the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of students to defend themselves against the dark arts.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5aOyriWkPec0zUDxmHFP9qMmBaj.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.684,NULL,NULL,'2018-04-30 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:19','675',138,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0373889','David Yates','Warner Bros. Pictures','Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix',22,NULL,NULL),(394,'Che: Part Two','2008-12-12','After the Cuban Revolution, Che is at the height of his fame and power. Then he disappears, re-emerging incognito in Bolivia, where he organizes a small group of Cuban comrades and Bolivian recruits to start the great Latin American Revolution. Through this story, we come to understand how Che remains a symbol of idealism and heroism that lives in the hearts of people around the world.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t9nH3bZf0Ezs2jwk0bTkvRr89Ao.jpg','movie',NULL,7,6.7,NULL,NULL,'2020-10-05 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:19','8880',135,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0374569','Steven Soderbergh','Wild Bunch','Che: Part Two',22,NULL,NULL),(395,'Kill Bill: Vol. 2','2004-04-16','The Bride unwaveringly continues on her roaring rampage of revenge against the band of assassins who had tried to kill her and her unborn child. She visits each of her former associates one-by-one, checking off the victims on her Death List Five until there\'s nothing left to do … but kill Bill.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2yhg0mZQMhDyvUQ4rG1IZ4oIA8L.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.876,NULL,NULL,'2019-10-14 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:19','393',136,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0378194','Robert Rodriguez','Super Cool ManChu','Kill Bill: Vol. 2',23,NULL,NULL),(396,'Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man\'s Chest','2006-07-06','Captain Jack Sparrow works his way out of a blood debt with the ghostly Davy Jones to avoid eternal damnation.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lAhc