is. The Basterds, lead by Lt. Aldo Raine soon cross paths with a French-Jewish teenage girl who runs a movie theater in Paris which is targeted by the soldiers.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7sfbEnaARXDDhKm0CZ7D7uc2sbo.jpg','movie',NULL,8,8.216,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:17','16869',153,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0361748','Quentin Tarantino','The Weinstein Company','Inglourious Basterds',23,NULL,NULL),(490,'The Machinist','2004-07-02','Trevor, an insomniac lathe operator, experiences unusual occurrences at work and home. A strange man follows him everywhere, but no one else seems to notice him.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/diAYqR4xdF9Hnj7qun6DEQhRrT2.jpg','movie',NULL,8,7.524,NULL,NULL,'2016-09-25 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:17','4553',101,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0361862','Brad Anderson','ICF','The Machinist',23,NULL,NULL),(491,'Oldboy','2003-11-21','With no clue how he came to be imprisoned, drugged and tortured for 15 years, a desperate businessman seeks revenge on his captors.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pWDtjs568ZfOTMbURQBYuT4Qxka.jpg','movie',NULL,8,8.266,NULL,NULL,'2019-04-15 00:00:00','2024-12-09 20:36:56','670',120,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0364569','Park Chan-wook','Show East','Oldboy',23,NULL,2),(492,'Casino Royale','2006-11-14','Le Chiffre, a banker to the world\'s terrorists, is scheduled to participate in a high-stakes poker game in Montenegro, where he intends to use his winnings to establish his financial grip on the terrorist market. M sends Bond—on his maiden mission as a 00 Agent—to attend this game and prevent Le Chiffre from winning. With the help of Vesper Lynd and Felix Leiter, Bond enters the most important poker game in his already dangerous career.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lMrxYKKhd4lqRzwUHAy5gcx9PSO.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.551,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:20','36557',144,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0381061','Martin Campbell','Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer','Casino Royale',22,NULL,NULL),(493,'Ratatouille','2007-06-28','Remy, a resident of Paris, appreciates good food and has quite a sophisticated palate. He would love to become a chef so he can create and enjoy culinary masterpieces to his heart\'s delight. The only problem is, Remy is a rat. When he winds up in the sewer beneath one of Paris\' finest restaurants, the rodent gourmet finds himself ideally placed to realize his dream.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t3vaWRPSf6WjDSamIkKDs1iQWna.jpg','movie',NULL,8,7.814,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-04 00:00:00','2024-02-01 21:47:20','2062',111,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0382932','Albert Lozano','Pixar','Ratatouille',20,NULL,NULL),(494,'Baby Driver','2017-06-28','After being coerced into working for a crime boss, a young getaway driver finds himself taking part in a heist doomed to fail.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rmnQ9jKW72bHu8uKlMjPIb2VLMI.jpg','movie',NULL,8,7.449,NULL,NULL,'2018-02-28 00:00:00','2024-12-09 20:44:53','339403',113,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3890160','Quentin Tarantino','Big Talk Productions','Baby Driver',23,NULL,NULL),(495,'Primer','2004-10-08','Friends and fledgling entrepreneurs invent a device in their garage which reduces the apparent mass of any object placed inside it, but they discover that it has some highly unexpected capabilities - ones that could enable them to do and to have seemingly anything they want. Taking advantage of this unique opportunity is the first challenge they face. Dealing with the consequences is the next.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xEoq2WmDzpzxhkHEsmOYOg6BPg6.jpg','movie',NULL,8,6.785,NULL,NULL,'2016-06-24 00:00:00','2024-02-12 23:20:09','14337',77,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0390384','Shane Carruth','Shane Carruth','Primer',22,NULL,3),(496,'Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince','2009-07-15','As Lord Voldemort tightens his grip on both the Muggle and wizarding worlds, Hogwarts is no longer a safe haven.