.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wjhUy9af89vc9CviKcPgTNTrmIq.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.702,NULL,NULL,'2024-02-05 04:36:59','2024-02-05 04:46:50','4978',80,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0090633','Steven Spielberg','Amblin Entertainment','An American Tail',20,NULL,NULL),(1196,'An American Tail: Fievel Goes West','1991-11-21','Some time after the Mousekewitz\'s have settled in America, they find that they are still having problems with the threat of cats. That makes them eager to try another home out in the west, where they are promised that mice and cats live in peace. Unfortunately, the one making this claim is an oily con artist named Cat R. Waul who is intent on his own sinister plan.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2XE34zwFf5MoZkKZ0p0Pp140GJt.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.29,NULL,NULL,'2024-02-05 04:37:29','2024-11-26 01:58:14','10380',75,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0101329','Steven Spielberg','Amblin Entertainment','An American Tail: Fievel Goes West',20,NULL,NULL),(1197,'There Will Be Blood','2007-12-26','Ruthless silver miner, turned oil prospector, Daniel Plainview, moves to oil-rich California. Using his son to project a trustworthy, family-man image, Plainview cons local landowners into selling him their valuable properties for a pittance. However, local preacher Eli Sunday suspects Plainview\'s motives and intentions, starting a slow-burning feud that threatens both their lives.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/spYrDOOLnkIfUOwTKKixC3h5j6G.jpg','movie',NULL,8,8.087,NULL,NULL,'2024-02-05 04:40:40','2024-02-12 23:17:54','7345',158,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0469494','Paul Thomas Anderson','Paramount Vantage','There Will Be Blood',23,NULL,2),(1198,'The Wonderful Story of Henry Sugar','2023-09-20','A rich man learns about a guru who can see without using his eyes. He sets out to master the skill in order to cheat at gambling.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fDUywEHwHh6nsLnVXAdPN9m4ZUG.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.292,NULL,NULL,'2024-02-07