9.3233,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-07 23:55:18','2024-03-07 23:56:17','b0b721ff-c388-4486-aa0f-c2b0bb321512',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/b0b721ff-c388-4486-aa0f-c2b0bb321512','Yamada Kanehito',NULL,'Sousou no Frieren',31,NULL,NULL),(1345,'Dragon Ball','1984-01-01','Dragon Ball follows the adventures of Goku from his childhood through adulthood as he trains in martial arts and explores the world in search of the seven mystical orbs known as the Dragon Balls, which can summon a wish-granting dragon when gathered. Along his journey, Goku makes several friends and battles a wide variety of villains, many of whom also seek the Dragon Balls for their own desires. Along the way becoming the strongest warrior in the universe.\n\nPart II (the post-time skip portion) of Dragon Ball is also known as \'Dragon Ball Z\' in North America.\n\n[Official English](https://www.viz.com/dragon-ball)\n\n---\n\n- **The 4th Best Selling Manga in History**','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/40bc649f-7b49-4645-859e-6cd94136e722/2a6d5eb3-e5e0-4fb8-a31d-04b816d6478a.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,8,8.98405,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-09 05:09:33','2024-03-09 05:25:22','40bc649f-7b49-4645-859e-6cd94136e722',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/40bc649f-7b49-4645-859e-6cd94136e722','Toriyama Akira',NULL,'Dragon Ball',32,NULL,NULL),(1346,'The Devil All the Time','2020-09-11','In Knockemstiff, Ohio and its neighboring backwoods, sinister characters converge around young Arvin Russell as he fights the evil forces that threaten him and his family.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bVL7LGq528h3KzeNI90HOVbV5uW.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.214,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-11 05:49:53','2024-03-11 20:36:12','499932',138,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt7395114','Antonio Campos','Nine Stories Productions','The Devil All the Time',23,NULL,NULL),(1347,'Poor Things','2023-12-07','Brought back to life by an unorthodox scientist, a young woman runs off with a debauched lawyer on a whirlwind adventure across the continents. Free from the prejudices of her times, she grows steadfast in her purpose to stand for equality and liberation.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kCGlIMHnOm8JPXq3rXM6c5wMxcT.jpg','movie',NULL,8,7.9,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-11 05:50:07','2024-10-11 18:53:59','792307',142,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt14230458','Yorgos Lanthimos','Searchlight Pictures','Poor Things',23,NULL,3),(1348,'Death Note','2003-01-01','A shinigami, as a god of death, can kill any person—provided they see their victim\'s face and write their victim\'s name in a notebook called a Death Note. One day, Ryuk, bored by the shinigami lifestyle and interested in seeing how a human would use a Death Note, drops one into the human realm.  \n  \nHigh school student and prodigy Light Yagami stumbles upon the Death Note and—since he deplores the state of the world—tests the deadly notebook by writing a criminal\'s name in it. When the criminal dies immediately following his experiment with the Death Note, Light is greatly surprised and quickly recognizes how devastating the power that has fallen into his hands could be.  \n  \nWith this divine capability, Light decides to extinguish all criminals in order to build a new world where crime does not exist and people worship him as a god. Police, however, quickly discover that a serial killer is targeting criminals and, consequently, try to apprehend the culprit. To do this, the Japanese in','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/75ee72ab-c6bf-4b87-badd-de839156934c/8f45c074-5512-4679-a14b-cac837c87171.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,9,8.8153,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-11 18:58:29','2024-03-11 18:58:49','75ee72ab-c6bf-4b87-badd-de839156934c',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/75ee72ab-c6bf-4b87-badd-de839156934c','Ohba Tsugumi',NULL,'Death Note',31,NULL,NULL),(1349,'All You Need Is Kill','2014-01-01','Since the alien Gitai invaded the Earth, humankind has been retreating. Now that Japan is almost surrounded by the Gitai, Keiji Kiriya is just one of many new recruits forced into a suit of battle armor and sent out to kill aliens. On a joint mission with the US special force led by Rita, known as the Bitch of the War, Keiji dies on the battlefield, only to find himself reborn.   \nAfter 4 times of \"death,\" Kiriya realizes that he has to win the battle to get out of the loop…  \n  \n**Notes:**   \n- [The 2014 movie \'Edge of Tomorrow\' starring Tom Cruise](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vw61gCe2oqI) is an adaptation of the original novel (with a different ending).  \n  \n [Official Vietnamese](https://www.fahasa.com/all-you-need-is-kill-cuoc-chien-luan-hoi-manga-bo-2-tap.html?attempt=1)','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/7dc523b0-8ecd-40b0-b86c-1ea57c07773c/5657cc26-67cf-4c2f-a338-dcb0a54500c3.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,7,8.72375,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-14 17:54:15',NULL,'7dc523b0-8ecd-40b0-b86c-1ea57c07773c',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/7dc523b0-8ecd-40b0-b86c-1ea57c07773c','Sakurazaka Hiroshi',NULL,'All You Need Is Kill',31,NULL,NULL),(1350,'Death Parade OP / Opening デス・パレード\"Flyers\" by BRADIO [HD 720p]','2015-03-16',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/UjjTMNDZi-A/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,9,9.91112,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-16 18:14:04',NULL,'UjjTMNDZi-A',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AD Anime',NULL,'Death Parade OP / Opening デス・パレード\"Flyers\" by BRADIO [HD 720p]',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UjjTMNDZi-A',NULL),(1352,'Freddy Got Fingered','2001-04-20','An unemployed cartoonist moves back in with his parents and younger brother Freddy. When his parents demand he leave, he begins to spread rumors that his father is sexually abusing Freddy.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gVmSZgxiT7ynyRLsEgg8Xs8ZVWX.jpg','movie',NULL,6,4.6,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-18 05:39:44','2025-03-10 08:52:23','13166',87,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0240515','Cristina Weigmann','Epsilon Motion Pictures','Freddy Got Fingered',23,NULL,2),(1353,'Gurren Lagann Opening','2017-03-18',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/FwgMxjhXkKo/maxres1.jpg','