e demise only to uncover a web of mystery that ultimately leads him deep into the heart of the surrounding woodland and his very own soul.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lA9CNSdo50iQPZ8A2fyVpMvJZAf.jpg','tv',NULL,6,8.3,NULL,NULL,'2024-03-28 17:36:45','2025-02-24 20:06:16','1920',NULL,48,3,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0098936','David Lynch','Spelling Entertainment','Twin Peaks',30,NULL,2),(1404,'Smiling Friends','2020-04-01','Smiling Friends Inc. is a small company whose main purpose is to bring happiness and make people smile. The series follows the day-to-day lives and misadventures of its representatives, the lazy, cynical Charlie, and the cheerful, optimistic Pim, as they try to cheer up and comfort the troubled people who call their company\'s hotline. They receive seemingly simple requests but the jobs turn out to be more complicated than they seem, making it difficult to bring happiness to the world.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xAJIdD5u9lo1RezhfcSq6s1jH2A.jpg','tv',NULL,8,8.1,NULL,NULL,'2024-04-02 04:27:10','2025-01-02 22:06:36','126506',NULL,12,2,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt12074628','Zach Hadel','Six Point Harness','Smiling Friends',30,NULL,NULL),(1405,'Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire','2024-03-27','Following their explosive showdown, Godzilla and Kong must reunite against a colossal undiscovered threat hidden within our world, challenging their very existence – and our own.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/phmjv93zEwitWLJEOvlXPhtK58o.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.755,NULL,NULL,'2024-04-06 06:47:34','2024-04-06 06:53:48','823464',115,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt14539740','Adam Wingard','Legendary Pictures','Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire',22,NULL,NULL),(1406,'The Lost World: Jurassic Park','1997-05-23','Four years after Jurassic Park\'s genetically bred dinosaurs ran amok, multimillionaire John Hammond shocks chaos theorist Ian Malcolm by revealing that he has been breeding more beasties at a secret location. Malcolm, his paleontologist ladylove and a wildlife videographer join an expedition to document the lethal lizards\' natural behavior in this action-packed thriller.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jElpCJkSaRPYwIMwZY28gOKV7BK.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.529,NULL,NULL,'2024-04-11 21:56:16',NULL,'330',129,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0119567','Steven Spielberg','Universal Pictures','The Lost World: Jurassic Park',22,NULL,NULL),(1407,'Balatro','2024-01-01','Balatro is a deck-building roguelite where you must play poker hands and earn chips to defeat enemy blinds. Enhance your deck of playing cards, buy Jokers to modify each hand you play, and discover new and wild synergies to win!','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co752b.jpg','game',NULL,8,8.83057,NULL,NULL,'2024-04-14 18:13:25',NULL,'251833',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/balatro',NULL,'LocalThunk','Balatro',35,NULL,NULL),(1408,'“Kaiju No. 8” Opening Theme Animation｜\'ABYSS\' by YUNGBLUD','2024-04-20',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/CFjI21M9wZs/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,7,9.6922,NULL,NULL,'2024-04-21 22:41:33',NULL,'CFjI21M9wZs',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,'TOHO animation チャンネル',NULL,'“Kaiju No. 8” Opening Theme Animation｜\'ABYSS\' by YUNGBLUD',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CFjI21M9wZs',NULL),(1409,'Overwatch 2 x Cowboy Bebop | Collaboration Trailer','2024-03-27',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/uS480mqndzQ/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,8,9.59611,NULL,NULL,'2024-04-27 16:41:45',NULL,'uS480mqndzQ',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,'PlayOverwatch',NULL,'Overwatch 2 x Cowboy Bebop | Collaboration Trailer',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uS480mqndzQ',NULL),(1410,'Triangle of Sadness','2022-09-18','A celebrity model couple are invited on a luxury cruise for the uber-rich, helmed by an unhinged, alcoholic captain. What first appears Instagrammable ends catastrophically, leaving the survivors stranded on a desert island in a struggle of hierarchy.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k9eLozCgCed5FGTSdHu0bBElAV8.jpg','movie',NULL,8,7.1,NULL,NULL,'2024-05-02 07:41:56','2024-11-11 20:34:11','497828',147,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt7322224','Ruben Östlund','30WEST','Triangle of Sadness',23,NULL,2),(1411,'Galaxy Quest','1999-12-25','For four years, the courageous crew of the NSEA protector - \"Commander Peter Quincy Taggart\" (Tim Allen), \"Lt. Tawny Madison (Sigourney Weaver) and \"Dr.Lazarus\" (Alan Rickman) - set off on a thrilling and often dangerous mission in space...and then their series was cancelled! Now, twenty years later, aliens under attack have mistaken the Galaxy Quest television transmissions for \"historical documents\" and beam up the crew of has-been actors to save the universe. With no script, no director and no clue, the actors must turn in the performances of their lives.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gh02DwQeLDbOPDXXySZxM9lc18k.jpg','movie',NULL,5,7.057,1,NULL,'2024-05-02 21:02:39','2024-05-02 21:03:07','926',101,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0177789','Dean Parisot','DreamWorks Pictures','Galaxy Quest',21,NULL,NULL),(1412,'Dune: Part Two','2024-02-27','Follow the mythic journey of Paul Atreides as he unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a path of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, Paul endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jKE4GGhhSLf4HR2fpD9Ayo2UtAD.jpg','movie',NULL,7,8.24,NULL,NULL,'2024-05-03 17:15:08','2026-03-17 17:38:38','693134',167,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt15239678','Denis Villeneuve','Legendary Pictures','Dune: Part Two',22,NULL,NULL),(1413,'Fantastic Mr. Fox','2009-10-23','The Fantastic Mr. Fox, bored with his current life, plans a heist against the three local farmers. The farmers, tired of sharing their chickens with the sly fox, seek revenge against him and his family.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t5v2Zsb5sa6PSP9jMUWY4GdIb3c.jpg','movie',NULL,