gan — known as Japan\'s greatest swordsman. So begins the story of intertwining fates, conflict, and strange destinies.  \n  \nNote:  \nIt\'s SHOUNEN because it\'s published in Champion Red, a shounen magazine for late teens+early 20ies','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/c8b3d40c-86b8-41cd-a793-c280d5b9da10/49fcbf1a-1a38-4f0a-8eca-ea5e38515465.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,8,8.58107,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-17 20:44:38',NULL,'c8b3d40c-86b8-41cd-a793-c280d5b9da10',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/c8b3d40c-86b8-41cd-a793-c280d5b9da10','Nanjou Norio',NULL,'Shigurui',31,NULL,NULL),(1422,'Love Bullet','2023-01-01','Since the dawn of humanity, those who have never experienced love and meet an untimely end are granted a second chance at life as Cupids by the Goddess of Love.\n\nPresent day Cupids have traded in their bow and arrow for modern firearms, but their mission remains the same: find suitable lovers for their targets and make them fall in love!','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/cb1b1da5-9436-49f5-8a6b-a1689fb86d91/0bcacc37-3c3a-482f-93cb-d67040b024be.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,6,8.86293,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-17 20:45:22',NULL,'cb1b1da5-9436-49f5-8a6b-a1689fb86d91',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/cb1b1da5-9436-49f5-8a6b-a1689fb86d91','inee',NULL,'Love Bullet',31,NULL,NULL),(1423,'How Do We Relationship?','2018-01-01','For as long as she’s known, Miwa’s been into women - and now she’s at university, it might finally be time for her to come out of her straight-passing shell. Of course, that takes a lot of confidence, and coming out is never easy - but could Saeko, her trashy popular weirdo of a friend, give her the help she needs - or just maybe, could the two of them be more alike than Miwa realises…?!  \r\n  \r\nThis series is a reimagining of tmfly’s earlier work of the same name.','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/9a0f1e7e-d84b-46e6-8596-ae5a60529e81/d6b93761-e0b6-456b-8a58-ce7440142678.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,8,8.29738,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-17 20:46:44','2024-07-05 23:52:04','9a0f1e7e-d84b-46e6-8596-ae5a60529e81',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/9a0f1e7e-d84b-46e6-8596-ae5a60529e81','tmfly',NULL,'How Do We Relationship?',32,NULL,NULL),(1424,'when you don\'t know the name of the song','2024-06-19',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/jZkGqlq8xwE/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,7,9.96363,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-19 20:50:39',NULL,'jZkGqlq8xwE',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Almost Friday TV',NULL,'when you don\'t know the name of the song',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jZkGqlq8xwE',NULL),(1425,'not in front of the babysitter','2024-06-12',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/oCv23s-hPKg/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,7,9.97521,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-19 21:53:44',NULL,'oCv23s-hPKg',8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Almost Friday TV',NULL,'not in front of the babysitter',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oCv23s-hPKg',NULL),(1426,'Peaked in High School','2024-06-05',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/Y4kKATFOrTM/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,9,9.97122,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-19 21:59:49',NULL,'Y4kKATFOrTM',6,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Almost Friday TV',NULL,'Peaked in High School',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y4kKATFOrTM',NULL),(1427,'Steven Universe Future','2019-12-07','After saving the universe, Steven is still at it, tying up every loose end. As he runs out of other people\'s problems to solve, he\'ll finally have to face his own.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/WtYiQk6432J0jCi61UQzLFtCCX.jpg','tv',NULL,8,8.176,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-22 17:14:33',NULL,'94280',NULL,20,1,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt13714610','Rebecca Sugar','Cartoon Network Studios','Steven Universe Future',28,NULL,NULL),(1428,'MASHLE: MAGIC AND MUSCLES The Divine Visionary Candidate Exam Arc | OPENING THEME','2024-01-24',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/9rVKos-oGnQ/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,8,9.90627,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-24 18:02:30',NULL,'9rVKos-oGnQ',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Aniplex USA',NULL,'MASHLE: MAGIC AND MUSCLES The Divine Visionary Candidate Exam Arc | OPENIN