 a muscular man named \'Rocky\'.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3pyE6ZqDbuJi7zrNzzQzcKTWdmN.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.5,NULL,NULL,'2024-07-25 08:06:21','2024-10-07 05:20:49','36685',100,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0073629','Graeme Clifford','Michael White Productions','The Rocky Horror Picture Show',23,NULL,2),(1434,'Clone High','2002-11-02','A group of high-school teens are the products of government employees\' secret experiment. They are the genetic clones of famous historical figures who have been dug up, re-created anew. Joan of Arc, Cleopatra, JFK, Gandhi, Abraham Lincoln and more are juxtaposed as teenagers dealing with teen issues in the 20th century.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gGRcBuEG3JlXWg5wTyeQtkXmPtY.jpg','tv',NULL,6,7.423,NULL,NULL,'2024-07-29 19:19:39','2024-07-29 19:20:38','2342',NULL,13,1,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0305011','Phil Lord','Lord Miller','Clone High',29,NULL,NULL),(1436,'Interstella 5555','2003-05-28','Four talented alien musicians are kidnapped by a record producer who disguises them as humans. Shep, a space pilot in love with bass player Stella, follows them to Earth. Reprogrammed to forget their real identities and renamed The Crescendolls, the group quickly becomes a huge success playing soulless corporate pop. At a concert, Shep manages to free all the musicians except Stella, and the band sets out to rediscover who they really are -- and to rescue Stella.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2lhOV8CCqsiGL1aIFvQzI0WLTek.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.8,NULL,NULL,'2024-07-30 17:42:57','2024-07-30 17:45:01','11049',66,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0368667','Daisuke Nishio','Toei Animation','Interstella 5555: The 5tory of the 5ecret 5tar 5ystem',21,NULL,NULL),(1437,'Despiser','2003-04-15','Having just been fired and dumped by his wife, life couldn\'t possibly be worse for independent artist Gordon Hauge (Mark Redfield)—until he wrecks his car and finds himself in purgatory, that is. Once there, he is attacked by fanatic Shadowmen and legions of Ragmen—souls being enslaved and bent to some dark purpose. Gordon is rescued by an eccentric band of freedom fighters, people from different times of history who lost their lives in noble sacrifice. They recruit the reluctant and befuddled Gordon and set off on a wild adventure through the surreal landscapes of purgatory to battle the Despiser—an evil being who now reigns in this seemingly God-abandoned halfway house north of hell and south of heaven.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p8T2KA4gbpPaH29eJKfEV9hDRCw.jpg','movie',NULL,3,5,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-11 09:09:06','2024-08-11 09:14:13','219808',105,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0349345','Philip J. Cook',NULL,'Despiser',23,NULL,NULL),(1438,'Sharknado','2013-07-11','A freak hurricane hits Los Angeles, causing man-eating sharks to be scooped up in tornadoes and flooding the city with shark-infested seawater. Surfer and bar-owner Fin sets out with his friends Baz and Nova to rescue his estranged wife April and teenage daughter Claudia.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/atEmHkVFTSGRYt2PeCiziQqbZnI.jpg','movie',NULL,1,3.916,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-11 09:09:28','2024-08-11 09:13:51','205321',86,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2724064','Anthony C. Ferrante','Syfy','Sharknado',23,NULL,NULL),(1439,'The Misty Green Sky','2016-01-18','A young girl on a far off planet in another solar system discovers that all she has been told is not true, her search for truth and love is an adventurous and cautionary tale.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dF6mS9vfaUDQcw8thzASdt6ukeM.jpg','movie',NULL,1,2,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-11 09:10:02','2024-08-11 09:11:30','499441',81,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6156136','Jack Foster','Kinonation','The Misty Green Sky',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1440,'Demon Haunt','2009-10-31','A school teacher and her wheelchair-bound sister purchase a house that seems to be haunted by a strange supernatural force. Father LeCleur and his son Raymond are called in to vanquish the demonic entities. But when the hell-spawn turn out to be much stronger than anyone thought, a bloody showdown ensues.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2kH3pZTUUVf6Azwobc6WMxhcriJ.jpg','movie',NULL,3,3,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-11 09:14:43',NULL,'301655',90,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1429446','Ted V. Mikels','TVM Global Entertainment','Demon Haunt',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1441,'Python','2000-08-09','Sleepy New Haven California is a small town with a big problem. A sixty foot slithering horror has arrived and shattered the town\'s tranquillity on it\'s path of death and destruction... Growing violent and more savage with each attack the gigantic creature soon becomes an unstoppable feeding machine raging beyond control of it\'s creator, leaving only the stripped bones of it\'s victims in it\'s wake.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lDbTpRHTRFWBK4j0FAWpE4M5WT2.jpg','movie',NULL,3,5.087,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-11 09:15:35','2024-08-11 09:17:37','41275',99,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0209264','Paul Bogh','Python Productions LLC','Python',23,NULL,NULL),(1442,'Mortal Kombat: Annihilation','1997-11-11','A group of heroic warriors has only six days to save the planet in \"Mortal Kombat Annihilation.\" To succeed they must survive the most spectacular series of challenges any human, or god, has ever encountered as they battle an evil warlord bent on taking control of Earth.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ttryglcY2osWZE3sRYBf3ewTZsW.jpg','movie',NULL,2,4.501,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-11 09:16:18','2024-08-11 09:17:30','9823',95,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0119707','John R. Leonetti','New Line Cinema','Mortal Kombat: Annihilation',22,NULL,NULL),(1443,'Manborg','2011-10-25','The evil Count Draculon and his army of demons have conquered Earth, but a young soldier who lost his life in the first war against Hell has reawakened in the future as MANBORG! Together with a crew of post-apocalyptic rebels, the half-man half-machine hero will fight to defeat Draculon and take back the planet!','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9iYzha3KcoS11EnRHBdmYaPqSVj.jpg','movie',NULL,3,4.845,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-11 09:16:47',NULL,'53101',70,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2060525','Steven Kostanski','Astron-6 Video International','Manborg',24,NULL,NULL),(1444,'Core Keeper','2022-01-01','Explore an endless cavern of creatures, relics and resources in a mining sandbox adventure for 1-8 players. Mine, build, fight, craft and farm to unravel the mystery of the ancient Core.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co396n.jpg','game',NULL,6,6.07937,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-12 18:14:51','2024-08-22 05:54:54','152127',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/core-keeper',NULL,'Pugstorm','Core Keeper',36,NULL,NULL),(1445,'Endless Space 2','2017-01-01','In Endless Space you play the role of the leader of one of the many intelligent beings of a galaxy at the beginning of the space age. Very quickly, you discover the remnants of an older civilization. That civilization called themselves the Endless, among their ruins, a matter called Dust with amazing proprieties is found. It shapes into whatever its user thinks of, it gives a reality to dreams… dreams that lead to the extinction of the Endless.\n\nSince then that matter became the most precious matter of the universe, and therefore the universal currency… but in front of the power of the Dust it is hard, even for the purest beings, not to fall under its charm…\n\nWe want the players to live an experience that goes beyond just strategy. You will live your own story of space conquest, with your own randomly generated galaxy full of civilizations, lifeforms, technologies and unknown worlds for you to conquer.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co2svr.jpg','game',NULL,8,8.20702,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-14 16:47:27','2024-08-22 05:55:02','11550',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/endless-space-2',NULL,'Amplitude Studios','Endless Space 2',36,NULL,NULL),(1446,'Memories','1995-12-2