for him.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2PI7Pcl77mOs0WnYFWrrYwooiHQ.jpg','movie',NULL,4,2.9,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-09 02:15:33','2024-11-12 07:57:01','88099',80,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0081572','Rene Martinez Jr.',NULL,'The Six Thousand Dollar Nigger',23,NULL,NULL),(1450,'American Commando Ninja','1988-12-16','David a young Ninja is recruited by his master to steal the formula for a viral weapon. He is pilled against two wily opponents - a KGB operative and Martin who has kidnapped the scientist who destroyed millions of lives through his bacterial experimentation in World War II and has developed the new lethal serum. Martin\'s intentions are not honest he wants the virus for himself in his bid to dominate the world.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jJ0aWCex0siwPAArZUKbKtTp7n4.jpg','movie',NULL,2,5.2,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-16 04:05:01','2024-09-16 04:06:32','105966',86,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2390225','Godfrey Ho','Adda Audio Visual Ltd.','American Commando Ninja',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1451,'Nightmare Weekend','1986-05-12','A female scientist performs experiments on three college girls that turn them into drooling, murderous mutants.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/z0gwiY1fE1zOTw7cvLEar0Ou87i.jpg','movie',NULL,4,3.726,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-16 04:05:27','2024-11-12 07:56:53','119592',86,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0091631','Henri Sala',NULL,'Nightmare Weekend',24,NULL,NULL),(1452,'Under the Waves','2023-01-01','Under the Waves is a narrative-driven adventure game about the engulfing power of grief. Set in the depths of the North Sea in a techno-futuristic 1970s, professional diver Stan is struggling to overcome a life-changing loss and embrace a new future. The isolation of the deep sea is a fitting manifestation of his state of mind, and as Stan retreads further into his self-imposed solitude, he starts to experience strange events far beneath the waves. Stuck between life and death, Stan will have to make the most significant choice of his existence.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co545p.jpg','game',NULL,6,6.99308,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-18 04:28:01','2024-09-18 04:28:50','214402',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/under-the-waves',NULL,'Parallel Studio','Under the Waves',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1453,'The Bear','2022-06-23','Carmy, a young fine-dining chef, comes home to Chicago to run his family sandwich shop. As he fights to transform the shop and himself, he works alongside a rough-around-the-edges crew that ultimately reveal themselves as his chosen family.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3MVHF64rlvH1eofKefIoazXwOK0.jpg','tv',NULL,6,8.309,1,NULL,'2024-09-22 02:21:27','2024-09-22 02:22:36','136315',NULL,28,3,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt14452776','Christopher Storer','FX Productions','The Bear',30,NULL,NULL),(1454,'American Hunter','1989-05-20','Jake Carver needs to retrieve a microfilm containing information which would cause a Wall Street panic and an economic crisis for Western governments. Also seeking the microfilm is the villainous Adam who plans to sell the microfilm to the highest bidder. Fist fights, explosions, and car chases ensue.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rjiD7BtqvJ1RfKG1NAQtyMFmROh.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.5,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-23 04:56:03','2024-11-18 01:11:26','89923',92,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0281587','Arizal','Rapi Films','American Hunter',24,NULL,NULL),(1455,'Hot to Trot','1988-08-26','Fred P. Chaney receives as inheritance after the death of his mother a speaking horse that also has good knowledge about the stock-market. With the help of this horse Fred gains a lot at the stock-market of Chicago.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A0GvohOiiWXc8LCqPu23KjdBiAa.jpg','movie',NULL,1,5.356,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-23 04:56:22','2024-09-23 04:58:48','30690',88,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0095326','Michael Dinner','Warner Bros. Pictures','Hot to Trot',21,NULL,NULL),(1456,'Splitgate','2019-01-01','Splitgate is a free-to-play, fast-paced multiplayer shooter that features player-controlled portals. This sci-fi shooter takes the FPS genre to a new dimension with its portal mechanics, delivering high-flying, multi-dimensional combat. Evoking memories of the most revered shooters of the past two decades, Splitgate embraces the classic and familiar feel of close-quarters combat while adding a unique twist.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co3cs5.jpg','game',NULL,6,6.83697,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-23 23:23:23',NULL,'114684',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/splitgate',NULL,'1047 Games','Splitgate',38,NULL,NULL),(1457,'Sable','2021-01-01','Sable is a coming-of-age tale of discovery through exploration across a strikingly rendered open world desert. Go on a deeply personal journey across an alien planet while learning its history and discovering Sable’s place in the world.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co3yzs.jpg','game',NULL,5,7.87402,1,NULL,'2024-09-25 02:31:50',NULL,'79995',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/sable',NULL,'Shedworks','Sable',35,NULL,NULL),(1458,'Heavy Is The Crown ft. Linkin Park (Official Music Video) | League of Legends Worlds 2024 Anthem','2024-09-25',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/5FrhtahQiRc/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,7,9.29185,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-26 10:22:39','2024-09-26 10:23:36','5FrhtahQiRc',4,NULL,NULL,NULL,'League of Legends',NULL,'Heavy Is The Crown ft. Linkin Park (Official Music Video) | League of Legends Worlds 2024 Anthem',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5FrhtahQiRc',NULL),(1459,'Pseudoregalia','2023-01-01','Sybil finds herself in a distorted castle and must find her own way out. Grow strong and unlock new abilities to build up a deep movement system, fight enemies, find secrets, and uncover the mysteries of Castle Sansa.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co7tz1.jpg','game',NULL,6,7.73049,1,NULL,'2024-09-27 06:21:41','2024-09-28 23:53:00','242148',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/pseudoregalia',NULL,'rittzler','Pseudoregalia',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1460,'Asparagus','1979-03-17','A symbolic reflection on issues of female sexuality, art and identity constructs.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vt5shhypt7fGzm1GslyUhCXN5dH.jpg','movie',NULL,2,6.635,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-03 05:26:06','2024-10-03 05:28:29','36881',20,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0140821','Suzan Pitt',NULL,'Asparagus',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Th3pu3QKC0&t=251s',NULL),(1461,'Penda\'s Fen','1974-03-21','Through a series of real and imagined encounters with angels, demons, and England\'s pagan past, a pastor\'s son begins to question his religion and politics, and comes to terms with his sexuality.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pKRibTfH0YgKbE3wVAKhhOWH9AZ.jpg','movie',NULL,1,7.5,NULL,1,'2024-10-04 19:13:44','2025-02-09 21:55:00','136611',92,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0325965','Alan Clarke','BBC','Penda\'s Fen',22,NULL,NULL),(1462,'The Blood on Satan\'s Claw','1971-01-28','The accidental unearthing of Satan’s earthly remains causes the children of a 17th-century English village to slowly convert into a coven of devil worshipers.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/spjOtYqkH4XouwC39lfcFmKl9T1.jpg','movie',NULL,4,6.13,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-04 19:16:49',NULL,'26774',97,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0066849','Piers Haggard','Tigon British Film Productions','The Blood on Satan\'s Claw',23,NULL,NULL),(1463,'Golden City','2016-01-01','<p>English digital series translating the original French series <a href=\"/golden-city/4050-40050/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-40050\">Golden City</a>.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/5514788-01.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 02:48:05',NULL,'95468',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/golden-city/4050-95468/','Delcourt',NULL,'Golden City',32,NULL,NULL),(1464,'Les Démons d\'Alexia','2004-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/77/1345786-380402.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 02:51:00',NULL,'34987',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-demons-dalexia/4050-34987/','Dupuis',NULL,'Les Démons d\'Alexia',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1465,'Gaston','1968-01-01','<br/>Original Gaston volume published by Dupuis in an extremely irregular way, reprinting extracts of older issues and adding unreleased material while continuing the original numbering, that already wasn\'t very logical.<br/> <br/>The volume actually started in 1960, but original Gaston issues from #0 to #5 are considered untraceable. Dupuis added new versions of them, gradually and slowly (5 issues in 16 years) in an attempt to fill holes in the numbering. This can be considered as the first Gaston volume, but also as the second, in a desperate try to put some order, excluding those 6 mysterious first issues that were \"replaced\" with a new #0 and new #R1 to #R5.<br/> <br/>The chronological publishing order, anyway, is: (0, 2, 3, 4, 1, 5) then 6, 7, 8, R1, 9, R2, 10, R3, 11, R4, 12, 13, 14, R0, R5, 15.<br/>Marsu Productions published the last issue, #15, in 1995. <br/>Any trace of chronological order is pure coincidence.','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/10/100758/1850712-segunda8.png','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 02:53:00','2024-10-05 06:49:44','40540',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/gaston/4050-40540/','Dupuis',NULL,'Gaston',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1466,'Marsupilami','1987-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/77/450547-marsupilami0capturez.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 02:54:10','2024-10-05 19:08:34','22187',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marsupilami/4050-22187/','Marsu Productions',NULL,'Marsupilami',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1469,'Jérôme K. Jérôme Bloche','1985-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11137/111371225/6759731-4924130500-97910.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 03:30:38','2024-10-05 06:50:41','116447',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/jerome-k-jerome-bloche/4050-116447/','Dupuis',NULL,'Jérôme K. Jérôme Bloche',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1470,'Aria','1982-01-01','<p>French series.</p><p>The series was created in 1982 and first published by Le Lombard, In 1994, it was republished by Dupuis in \"Collection repérages\". Aria\'s adventures have been published in \"Spirou Magazine\" from 2002 to 2004. She came back in the magazine in 2010 where all her new adventures will be pre-published before appearing on an album.</p><p>Aria is a lonely Amazon and courageous warrior. She travels from country to country, in a fantastic Middle Ages where disturbing practices of magic and witchcraft take place. Knight without armor, she has a sense of honor. Sensual beauty, she has a sense of celebration and pleasure. She carries high the banner of independence and freedom in a world cruel to women. But she loves life. Above all.</p><div> </div>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11119/111191703/7928534-ar17.jpg','comic',NULL,5,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 03:44:11','2024-10-05 06:51:50','135512',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/aria/4050-135512/','Le Lombard',NULL,'Aria',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1471,'Boule & Bill','2008-01-01','<p>French series.</p><h4>Publishers</h4><ul><li>Dupuis (Tome 1-24)</li><li>Dargaud (Tome 25+)</li></ul>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/4064712-01.jpg','comic',NULL,5,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 03:44:38','2024-10-05 06:51:56','70187',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/boule-bill/4050-70187/','Dargaud',NULL,'Boule & Bill',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1472,'Yoko Tsuno','1972-01-01','<figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.comicvine.com/a/uploads/original/11119/111191703/7865162-yoko.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-7865162\" data-ratio=\"1.885\" data-width=\"400\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 400px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:188.5%\" href=\"https://www.comicvine.com/a/uploads/original/11119/111191703/7865162-yoko.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-7865162\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_small/11119/111191703/7865162-yoko.png\" srcset=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/11119/111191703/7865162-yoko.png 400w, https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_small/11119/111191703/7865162-yoko.png 339w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 339px) 100vw, 339px\" data-width=\"339\"></a></figure><p>Ongoing original French series.</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/yoko-tsuno/4050-87872/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-87872\">German translation</a> by <a href=\"/carlsen-comics/4010-246/\" data-ref-','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11136/111361767/7134608-couv_49289.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:02:48',NULL,'122646',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/yoko-tsuno/4050-122646/','Dupuis',NULL,'Yoko Tsuno',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1473,'L\'Agent 212','1981-01-01','<p>French edition.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11/110017/2721236-www.jpg','comic',NULL,5,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:24:21','2024-10-05 06:51:46','54286',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/lagent-212/4050-54286/','Dupuis',NULL,'L\'Agent 212',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1474,'Cédric','1989-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/77/1345793-380364.jpg','comic',NULL,5,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:24:36','2024-10-05 06:51:16','29461',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/cedric/4050-29461/','Dupuis',NULL,'Cédric',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1475,'Benoît Brisefer','1962-01-01','<figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/6/67663/6673685-4674824835-benoi.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-6673685\" data-ratio=\"1.4030769230769\" data-width=\"325\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 325px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:140.3%\" href=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/6/67663/6673685-4674824835-benoi.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-6673685\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/6/67663/6673685-4674824835-benoi.jpg\" srcset=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/6/67663/6673685-4674824835-benoi.jpg 325w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 456px) 100vw, 456px\" data-width=\"456\"></a></figure><p>French series.</p><p><em>A première vue, rien ne distingue Benoît Brisefer des autres petits garçons de son âge. Pourtant, Benoît est doué d\'une force herculéenne ! Tous les vauriens qu\'il croise sur son chemin en sont pour leurs frais. Mais hélas, personne n\'est parfai','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/5577237-08.jpg','comic',NULL,6,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:24:52','2024-10-06 19:15:36','96391',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/benoit-brisefer/4050-96391/','Le Lombard',NULL,'Benoît Brisefer',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1476,'Les Tuniques Bleues','1972-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/5578963-29.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:25:29','2024-10-05 19:10:37','84633',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-tuniques-bleues/4050-84633/','Dupuis',NULL,'Les Tuniques Bleues',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1478,'Lucky Luke','1949-01-01','<p>Original Lucky Luke\'s volume, published by Dupuis from 1949 to 1967. Rene Goscinny wrote issue #9 and stayed as a writer since issue #11.</p><p>From issue #32 (although it can be found as a new issue #1) until issue #59 (or #28) Dargaud continued the volume, including the last issue written by Goscinny, #46 (or #15), in 1977.</p><p>Lucky Production published from issue #60 (or #29) until issue #67 (or #36).</p><p>Lucky Comics continued publishing it until last issue, #70 (or #39), in 2002.</p><p>After the death of artist Morris, Lucky Comics started a <a href=\"https://www.comicvine.com/les-aventures-de-lucky-lucke/4050-40534/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-40534\">new volume</a>.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/10/100758/1846104-dar26.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:34:43','2024-10-05 19:09:45','32180',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/lucky-luke/4050-32180/','Lucky Comics',NULL,'Lucky Luke',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1479,'Spirou & Fantasio','2009-01-01','<p>A series starring <a data-ref-id=\"4005-38886\" href=\"/spirou/4005-38886/\" slug=\"spirou\">Spirou</a>.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/3498129-02.jpg','comic',NULL,9,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:37:12',NULL,'52103',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/spirou-fantasio/4050-52103/','Cinebook',NULL,'Spirou & Fantasio',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1480,'Le Petit Spirou','1990-01-01','<figure data-align=\"right\" data-embed-type=\"image\" data-img-src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/6/69755/1962880-tispi_nl.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-1962880\" data-size=\"medium\" data-ratio=\"0.4602510460251\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:46.0%\" href=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/6/69755/1962880-tispi_nl.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-1962880\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/6/69755/1962880-tispi_nl.jpg\" srcset=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/6/69755/1962880-tispi_nl.jpg 239w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 239px) 100vw, 239px\" data-width=\"239\"></a></figure><p>Le Petit Spirou is a French comic book about the populair French comic book character <a href=\"../../spirou/29-38886/\" rel=\"nofollow \">Spirou</a>. These books are filled with short stories about the character\'s childhood. It\'s published by <a href=\"../../dupuis/57-2368/\" rel=\"nofollow \">Dupuis</a> in 1990 and written by <a href=\"../../tom','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/69755/1962976-cover08.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,