00758/1834903-soda8.jpg','comic',NULL,9,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:47:10',NULL,'40396',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/soda/4050-40396/','Dupuis',NULL,'Soda',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1491,'Plunk!','2007-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/4/40363/1745696-01.jpg','comic',NULL,5,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:48:26',NULL,'24022',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/plunk/4050-24022/','Dupuis',NULL,'Plunk!',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1492,'Zarla','2011-01-01','<br/>German adventure comic.','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/3125/2128488-zarla1.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:49:05','2024-10-05 18:47:30','44619',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/zarla/4050-44619/','Piredda Verlag',NULL,'Zarla',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1493,'Ralph Azham','2012-01-01','<table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><em>Mit seiner seherischen Gabe bringt Ralph Azham regelmäßig das ganze Dorf gegen sich auf. Als das heilige Orakel ihm die Anerkennung zum Auserwählten verweigert, und er auch noch den Ältestenrat verärgert, ist er endgültig unten durch und landet bei den Schweinen. Doch dann wird das Dorf von einer Horde blutrünstiger Krieger überfallen, und Ralph Azham erhält Gelegenheit, sich zu beweisen.</em><br /><br /><em> Lewis Trondheims neue Serie »Ralph Azham« hat alle Qualitäten, die zahlreichen Fans seines »Donjon«-Universums zu beglücken: Eine farbenfrohe Fantasiewelt, einen sympathischen Antihelden und aberwitzige Dialoge.</em></td></tr><tr><td> </td><td> </td></tr></tbody></table>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/3125/4710339-ral4.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:50:17','2024-10-05 06:50:49','83422',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/ralph-azham/4050-83422/','Reprodukt',NULL,'Ralph Azham',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1494,'Zombillénium','2010-01-01','<p>French language series.</p><p><i>At the Zombillénium theme park, people are only hired for the long term. The selection criteria aren\'t very stringent, only mere mortals are refused. Francis von Bloodt, a vampire, paternally manages this little crisis-free business... An impeccable black comedy from the pen of Arthur de Pins.</i></p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/3584853-03.jpg','comic',NULL,9,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:53:02','2024-10-05 19:03:52','39267',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/zombillenium/4050-39267/','Dupuis',NULL,'Zombillénium',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1495,'Les Nombrils','2006-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/3652493-01.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:53:29',NULL,'71831',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-nombrils/4050-71831/','Dupuis',NULL,'Les Nombrils',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1496,'Cupidon','1990-01-01','<p>French series.</p><p>Cupid is a little angel with the appearance of a little winged boy, who shoots his arrows as he pleases, and gives birth to the hottest passions and the most unexpected unions. Fortunately, Saint Peter is there to watch him.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11119/111191703/8144165-6035423019-cupid.jpg','comic',NULL,6,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:54:03',NULL,'138777',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/cupidon/4050-138777/','Dupuis',NULL,'Cupidon',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1497,'Les Campbell','2014-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/6160108-01.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:54:32','2024-10-05 19:08:47','91677',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-campbell/4050-91677/','Dupuis',NULL,'Les Campbell',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1498,'Le Royaume','2009-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11119/111191703/9332979-7729508921-album.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:55:41',NULL,'157676',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/le-royaume/4050-157676/','Dupuis',NULL,'Le Royaume',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1499,'Seuls','2006-01-01','<p>\"Seuls\" (Alone) tell the adventures of five children aged 5, 8, 9, 10 and 12 who wake up one day and find a big city absolutely empty. They will have to survive on their own and find out what happened to everybody. </p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/6750318-1782896372-97828.jpg','comic',NULL,9,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:59:39',NULL,'40655',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/seuls/4050-40655/','Rue de Sèvres',NULL,'Seuls',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1500,'Louca','2013-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/6199683-01.jpg','comic',NULL,6,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 04:59:59',NULL,'107279',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/louca/4050-107279/','Dupuis',NULL,'Louca',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1501,'Les cavaliers de l\'apocadispe','2019-01-01','<figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"medium\" data-img-src=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/11119/111191703/8064998-x.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-8064998\" data-ratio=\"0.46859296482412\" data-width=\"796\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 796px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:46.9%\" href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/11119/111191703/8064998-x.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-8064998\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/11119/111191703/8064998-x.png\" srcset=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/11119/111191703/8064998-x.png 796w, https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11119/111191703/8064998-x.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 796px) 100vw, 796px\" data-width=\"796\"></a></figure><p>French series.</p><p>From 2008, the Journal SPIROU welcomes this small band of troublemakers larger than life, led by Libon. Short stories with unclassifiable, unbridled, extreme humor, which we find','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11119/111191703/8064999-2.