pulateur et peu scrupuleux…Mais le comte de Saunhac est-il réellement mort ?…La quête de messire Guillaume ne fait que commencer !','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51Ht+P8DI7L._SY445_SX342_.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:17:36',NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.dupuis.com/messire-guillaume/bd/messire-guillaume-tome-1-les-contrees-lointaines/3809',' Matthieu Bonhomme',NULL,'Messire Guillaume',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1507,'Marzi','2017-01-01','<p>English digital translation.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/6006848-02.jpg','comic',NULL,5,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:18:13','2024-10-05 06:51:38','102798',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marzi/4050-102798/','Europe Comics',NULL,'Marzi',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1508,'Les Naufragés d’Ythaq','2005-01-01','<p>A luxurious cruise vessel crashes on Ythaq, among the survivors, a young and intrepid astro-navigator, a poetic technician and a beautiful passenger. Stalked by pitiless mercenaries, they are going to discover a medieval world where many different species live together in amazing harmony. But, are the shipwrecks accidental? What terrible secret is hidden behind the walls and the doors of the palaces of Ythaq?</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/3415299-01.jpg','comic',NULL,6,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:19:55',NULL,'42717',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-naufrages-d-ythaq/4050-42717/','Soleil',NULL,'Les Naufragés d’Ythaq',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1509,'The World According To François','2019-01-01','<p>English digital translation.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/7107341-01.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:20:41',NULL,'121984',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/the-world-according-to-francois/4050-121984/','Europe Comics',NULL,'The World According To François',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1510,'Zoo','1994-01-01','<p>The  madness  of  men  spreading  death .  In  Normandy ,  where  the zoo  saw  less and  less like  a  paradise ,  the  echo  of  the  war approaches .  For  Anna ,  Celestin ,  Buggy  and  Manon  is the beginning  of  uncertain times .  And  the zoo ,  men  and  beasts  will soon  at  the heart  of  the  storm.<br/> A  series  steeped  in  strength ,  emotion  and beauty .    </p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/7/73434/1803554-zoo03.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:22:18',NULL,'39935',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/zoo/4050-39935/','Dupuis',NULL,'Zoo',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1511,'Ange & Diablesses','2009-01-01','<p>French publication.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11/110017/7891860-angeetdiablesses%5B1%5D%2800.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:26:12',NULL,'134909',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/ange-and-diablesses/4050-134909/','Dupuis',NULL,'Ange & Diablesses',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1512,'Esteban','2015-01-01','<p>English digital translation.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/5557052-03.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:26:41',NULL,'95995',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/esteban/4050-95995/','Europe Comics',NULL,'Esteban',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1513,'Sale bête','2012-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/3125/6705378-sal1.jpg','comic',NULL,4,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:30:54','2025-01-02 07:46:31','115616',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/sale-bete/4050-115616/','Dupuis',NULL,'Sale bête',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1514,'Les Brigades du Temps','2012-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11129/111297164/6218409-1.jpg','comic',NULL,6,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:31:25',NULL,'107555',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-brigades-du-temps/4050-107555/','Dupuis',NULL,'Les Brigades du Temps',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1515,'Blacksad','2000-01-01','<p>Spanish series translated in French.</p><h4><strong>English Language Editions</strong></h4><ul><li><a href=\"/blacksad/4050-61907/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-61907\">Blacksad</a> (#1-2) (iBooks)</li><li><a href=\"/blacksad/4050-33631/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-33631\">Blacksad</a> (#1-3)</li><li><a href=\"/blacksad-silent-hell/4050-50368/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-50368\">Blacksad: Silent Hell</a> (#4)</li><li><a href=\"/blacksad-amarillo/4050-77410/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-77410\">Blacksad: Amarillo</a> (#5)</li><li><a href=\"/blacksad/4050-95981/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-95981\">Blacksad</a> (#1-5) (Europe Comics)</li></ul>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11119/111191703/8183651-8410355631-Couv_.jpg','comic',NULL,9,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:34:33',NULL,'26644',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/blacksad/4050-26644/','Dargaud',NULL,'Blacksad',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1516,'Champignac','2019-01-01','<p>French series.</p><p>Prequel de <a href=\"/spirou-et-fantasio/4050-27780/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-27780\">Spirou et Fantasio</a></p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/7984830-01.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:38:18',NULL,'136223',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/champignac/4050-136223/','Dupuis',NULL,'Champignac',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1517,'Asterix','1968-01-01','<p>Published in Germany since 1968.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/13/137711/2678418-a__dldc_018_pagecover.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:41:07','2024-10-05 19:20:59','53586',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/asterix/4050-53586/','Egmont Ehapa Verlag',NULL,'Asterix',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1518,'Idées Noires - L\'intégrale complète','2020-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11111/111117470/7740885-img20210101_09161804.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:41:22',NULL,'132914',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/idees-noires-lintegrale-complete/4050-132914/','Fluide Glacial',NULL,'Idées Noires - L\'intégrale complète',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1519,'The Adventures of Tintin','1974-01-01','<p>This volume covers the English translated publication of the <a href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-aventures-de-tintin/4050-32164/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-32164\">Belgian original</a>. Issues were published out of order.</p><p><em>Tintin is a journalist who always keeps getting into strange and dangerous situations, but always manages to overcome them, albeit with the help of his friends.</em></p><p>Tintin started as a comic strip character in 1929. The strips were later collected in albums. His adventures first appeared in Belgium in 1946 published by Le Lombard publishers, each of his adventures have reprinted many times, as well as being translated into dozens of languages, including English by Little Brown and Company, however Le Lombard is still his home.</p><p><strong>Related publication:</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"/herge-the-adventures-of-tintin/4050-86083/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-86083\">Hergé - The Adventures of Tintin</a></li></ul>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/2/25521/717461-tintin_cover___explorers_on_the_moon.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:43:23',NULL,'21843',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/the-adventures-of-tintin/4050-21843/','Casterman',NULL,'The Adventures of Tintin',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1520,'Les Aventures de Blake et Mortimer','1946-01-01','<p>Born of <a href=\"/edgar-pierre-jacobs/4040-55866/\" data-ref-id=\"4040-55866\">Edgar Pierre Jacobs</a>’ imagination during the post-WWII period, <a href=\"/mortimer/4005-4008/\" data-ref-id=\"4005-4008\">Professor Philip Mortimer</a>, nuclear physicist, and <a href=\"/blake/4005-4009/\" data-ref-id=\"4005-4009\">Captain</a> <a href=\"/blake/4005-4009/\" data-ref-id=\"4005-4009\">Francis Blake</a>, dashing head of MI5, are legendary heroes of the Franco-Belgian industry. The author, a close collaborator of <a href=\"/herge/4040-45908/\" data-ref-id=\"4040-45908\">Hergé</a>, appreciated the excessive and the astonishing that could be found within the scope of scientific invention; his heroes, very much ahead of their time, discover extraordinary objects and phenomena through their uncommon adventures. Before devoting himself exclusively to them, Jacobs collaborated with Hergé and took part in the making of “<a href=\"/the-adventures-of-tintin-tintin-in-the-congo/4000-152576/\" data-ref-id=\"4000-152576\">Ti','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/13/130983/2528573-9782870970102.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:44:06',NULL,'51195',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-aventures-de-blake-et-mortimer/4050-51195/','Les Éditions Blake et Mortimer',NULL,'Les Aventures de Blake et Mortimer',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1521,'Lanfeust de Troy','1994-01-01','<h2>The Universe of Troy</h2><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"medium\" data-img-src=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/11119/111191703/7963435-troybandeau.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-7963435\" data-ratio=\"0.33726812816189\" data-width=\"1186\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1186px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:33.7%\" href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/11119/111191703/7963435-troybandeau.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-7963435\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11119/111191703/7963435-troybandeau.jpg\" srcset=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/11119/111191703/7963435-troybandeau.jpg 1186w, https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/11119/111191703/7963435-troybandeau.jpg 960w, https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11119/111191703/7963435-troybandeau.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\" data-width=\"480\"></a></figure><p>All thes','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11144/111447612/7884332-81rg9ycekal.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:44:33',NULL,'134790',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/lanfeust-de-troy/4050-134790/','Soleil',NULL,'Lanfeust de Troy',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1522,'Léonard','1977-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/5979442-20.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:45:34',NULL,'85349',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/leonard/4050-85349/','Le Lombard',NULL,'Léonard',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1523,'Le Chat','1986-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11134/111344525/8209148-3401782236-71L1x.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:46:13',NULL,'139706',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/le-chat/4050-139706/','Casterman',NULL,'Le Chat',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1524,'Yakari','1973-01-01','<p>French series.</p><p><em>Yakari est un enfant sioux heureux, courageux et généreux. Dans le monde enchanteur de La Grande Prairie, Yakari chevauche d\'aventures en aventures, de rencontres en rencontres...</em></p><p><em>Souvent confronté au danger, il fait l\'apprentissage de la vie. Doté du fabuleux pouvoir de parler et de comprendre le langage des animaux, le petit Indien dialogue avec eux afin de mieux les connaître et de les respecter. Animé d\'un profond sens de l\'amitié, il se met à l\'écoute de leurs problèmes et leur vient en aide.</em></p><p><em>Respect des autres et de la nature, amitié, courage,... A travers cette série indémodable, Derib et Job évoquent des valeurs qui parlent à tous les enfants.</em></p><h4>Publishers</h4><ul><li>Dargaud</li><li>Rossel</li><li>24 heures</li><li>Casterman</li><li>Le Lombard</li></ul>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/5580724-01.jpg','comic',NULL,5,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:47:09','2024-10-05 06:51:42','96543',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/yakari/4050-96543/','Le Lombard',NULL,'Yakari',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1525,'Olivier Rameau','1997-01-01','<p><em>Un jeune homme \"frais et beau\" découvre en compagnie de la ravissante Colombe Tiredaile, le monde de Rêverose, où tout n\'est que rêve et fantaisie.</em></p><p><em>C\'est joli, frais et très poétique.</em></p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11134/111344525/8211264-3330791703-Couv_.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:47:48',NULL,'139715',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/olivier-rameau/4050-139715/','P&T Production',NULL,'Olivier Rameau',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1526,'Calvin et Hobbes','1991-01-01',NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11134/111344525/8212818-9992153088-Couv_.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:49:18',NULL,'139741',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/calvin-et-hobbes/4050-139741/','Editions Hors Collection',NULL,'Calvin et Hobbes',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1527,'La Jeunesse de Picsou','1998-01-01','<p>French series.</p><p>With issue #3 the series title changes to <a href=\"https://www.comicvine.com/les-tresors-de-picsou/4050-68505/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-68505\">Les Trésors de Picsou</a>.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/3392892-01.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:49:36',NULL,'68504',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/la-jeunesse-de-picsou/4050-68504/','Hachette',NULL,'La Jeunesse de Picsou',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1528,'Les Trésors de Picsou','2006-01-01','<p>French series.</p><p>Numbering continues from <a href=\"//www.comicvine.com/la-jeunesse-de-picsou/4050-68504/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-68504\">La Jeunesse de Picsou</a>.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/67663/3392907-09.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 05:49:56',NULL,'68505',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-tresors-de-picsou/4050-68505/','Hachette',NULL,'Les Trésors de Picsou',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1529,'Noir Burlesque','2021-01-01','<p>2 part mini series</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11122/111221019/8288905-8639754067-97903.jpg','comic',NULL,7,0,NU