2024-10-05 19:01:33',NULL,'128859',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/izunas-integrale/4050-128859/','Les Humanoïdes Associés',NULL,'Izunas: Intégrale',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1543,'Les Schtroumpfs','1963-01-01','<p>Who does not know the Smurfs? These nice little blue characters with big white hats all look the same, even though they have their own personality and speak a curious language in which the majority of words are replaced by \"smurf\".</p><h4>Publishers</h4><ul><li>1-13 published by Dupuis</li><li>14-current published by Le Lombard</li></ul><h4>Collected in</h4><ul><li><p><a href=\"/les-schtroumpfs-lintegrale/4050-143978/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-143978\">Les Schtroumpfs - L\'intégrale</a></p></li></ul>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/6/62795/3712892-schtroumpfsles07.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 19:07:38',NULL,'71000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/les-schtroumpfs/4050-71000/','Dupuis',NULL,'Les Schtroumpfs',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1544,'Spirou et Fantasio','1950-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/5/51294/948525-9782800138442_g.jpg','comic',NULL,9,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-05 19:14:52',NULL,'27780',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/spirou-et-fantasio/4050-27780/','Dupuis',NULL,'Spirou et Fantasio',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1545,'Gachiakuta','2022-01-01','A slum where criminals\' descendants live... People beyond the border look down and discriminate them as \"tribal people.\" Ludo, an orphan boy, lives in the slum with his foster parent, Legt, and makes a living using his extraordinary physical abilities. However, one day, he was accused for a crime he didn\'t commit., and is thrown into the \"abyss\" which even the slum people fear.\n\n---\nLiving in the slums of a wealthy town, Rudo and his foster father Legto try to coexist with the rest of the town\'s residents, but Rudo despises the wastefulness of the upper class. Ignoring the warnings from those around him, Rudo regularly rummages through the town\'s garbage in search of anything useful or valuable to save from the \"Abyss\"—a massive hole where anything considered trash is dumped, including people. Rudo\'s biological father was one such person, having been thrown into the Abyss after he was accused of murder.\n\nOne day, after running into a mysterious figure on the way home, Rudo returns to f','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/192aa767-2479-42c1-9780-8d65a2efd36a/f5401d33-46db-43ee-8ef9-8001ab08e127.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,7,8.99835,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-06 19:14:39',NULL,'192aa767-2479-42c1-9780-8d65a2efd36a',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/192aa767-2479-42c1-9780-8d65a2efd36a','Urana Kei',NULL,'Gachiakuta',32,NULL,NULL),(1546,'Suspiria','1977-02-01','An American newcomer to a prestigious German ballet academy comes to realize that the school is a front for something sinister amid a series of grisly murders.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5ya8jTbNZTrCFUx9OwpNBjCivXY.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.503,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-07 05:17:15','2024-10-07 05:20:15','11906',99,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0076786','Dario Argento','Seda Spettacoli','Suspiria',23,NULL,2),(1547,'Voices of the Void','2022-01-01','You work as a scientist in the isolated research lab in the mountains of Switzerland. Your task is to gather signals from space, analyze them, process them and sell them to get points.\n\nYou can get regular signals and objects like dwarf planets and stars, or you can get something \"unusual\" or \"strange\"','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co5qlp.jpg','game',NULL,7,9.7208,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-07 18:12:18',NULL,'224415',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/voices-of-the-void--1',NULL,NULL,'Voices of the Void',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1548,'Urban','2013-01-01','<p>German translation.</p><p><em>2058. Zachary Buzz verlässt den elterlichen Bauernhof, um nach Myjoy zu gehen. Myjoy ist eine gigantische Stadt, in der sich alles nur ums Amüsement dreht. Sein Traum ist es, den Urban Interceptors beizutreten, der besten Polizei der Welt.</em></p><p><em>Myjoy ist ein totalitärer Staat, in dem jede Bewegung der Bewohner verfolgt wird. Und doch werden immer wieder junge Frauen ermordet, deren verstümmelte Leichen man in den finsteren Ecken der Stadt findet. Als dann auch noch der ermittelnde Beamte ermordet wird, soll Isham El Ghellab, der beste Urban Interceptor, den Fall zu lösen – und die Jagd nach dem Mörder wird als dramatisches TV-Game inszeniert, an dem die Zuschauer beteiligt sind.</em></p><p><em>Hochintelligente Science Fiction für anspruchsvolle Comic-Liebhaber in ausgefallener Grafik.</em></p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11116/111168846/5752074-urban01_comicbude_001.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-07 18:16:07','2024-10-07 18:16:22','99922',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/urban/4050-99922/','Splitter',NULL,'Urban',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1549,'Horde du Contrevent','2017-01-01','<p>French series.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11134/111344525/8244473-5735756753-91x2v.jpg','comic',NULL,8,0,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-07 18:18:25','2025-01-02 07:45:39','105188',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/horde-du-contrevent/4050-105188/','Delcourt',NULL,'Horde du Contrevent',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1550,'Pieces','1982-08-23','A frustrated Boston detective searches for the maniac responsible for mutilating a number of university coeds.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pYviMR1o0g8VMUZJK5WTvnZBS2g.jpg','movie',NULL,4,5.9,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-13 20:51:48',NULL,'47886',85,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0082748','Juan Piquer Simón','Almena Films','Pieces',23,NULL,NULL),(1551,'Blood Harvest','1987-01-01','A beautiful young girl returns to her peaceful rural home town to find that the house she grew up in has been defaced, her parents are missing, and the whole town hates her father, a bank supervisor who foreclosed on many of the local farms. Only \"Marvelous Mervo,\" who wanders around town dressed in a clown\'s suit with a permanent grin painted on his face, seems happy to see her. As Mervo\'s brother tries to rekindle his love affair with Jill, those closest to her are slaughtered like cattle, one by one.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8XoHxBdM0ygdK1VBksgzwAMwkCy.jpg','movie',NULL,3,4.4,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-13 20:52:28',NULL,'78068',87,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0092671','Bill Rebane',NULL,'Blood Harvest',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1552,'Deadly Manor','1990-03-07','A group of teenagers take refuge in an old, deserted mansion. Soon the members of the group start turning up dead, and the teenagers realize that they\'re not alone in the mansion.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4J7ytnXbKcZU6dXWZyuUXudo2nQ.jpg','movie',NULL,3,5.2,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-13 20:52:47','2024-10-13 20:54:47','128188',87,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0099381','José Ramón Larraz','Filmworld International','Deadly Manor',23,NULL,NULL),(1553,'Horror Brunch','1987-05-11','A brunch turns deadly.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzE4M2NlZjAtYTJhYS00ZjIzLWFiMWItNmM3ODJmZTlmYjUyXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.1,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-13 20:54:28','2024-10-13 20:55:53','211266',5,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0379315','Rik Carter',NULL,'Horror Brunch',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1554,'Death Nurse 2','1988-01-01','That crazy killer nurse is at it again! Edith Mortley continues to slay more and more dumbfounded patients, turning them into rat food.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2HsgmvE3mK4k5RaB0nFSRexGhEd.jpg','movie',NULL,1,3.5,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-16 04:55:44',NULL,'179496',62,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0257525','Nick Millard',NULL,'Death Nurse 2',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1555,'Eyes Without a Face','1960-01-11','Dr. Génessier is riddled with guilt after an accident that he caused disfigures the face of his daughter, the once beautiful Christiane, who outsiders believe is dead. Dr. Génessier, along with ac