hicago nightclub.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bvpLcoETKKVb6iFyl5r47pQKKsh.jpg','movie',NULL,3,5.5,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-26 15:38:58',NULL,'28170',81,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0068649','Herschell Gordon Lewis','Lewis Motion Picture Enterprisee','The Gore Gore Girls',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1570,'Godzilla 1985','1985-08-23','Originally released in Japan as \"The Return of Godzilla\"  in 1984, this is the heavily re-edited, re-titled \"Godzilla 1985\".  Adding in new footage of Raymond Burr, this 16th Godzilla film ignores all previous sequels and serves as a direct follow-up to the 1956 \"Godzilla King of the Monsters\", which also featured scenes with Burr edited into 1954\'s \"Godzilla\". This film restores the darker tone of the original, as we witness the nuclear destruction of giant lizard terrorizing Japan.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/blKtf1L6LA3mFW8aVJzxnaI8CLn.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.7,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-26 15:39:21',NULL,'39256',87,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0087344','Tony Randel','Toho Pictures','Godzilla 1985',21,NULL,NULL),(1571,'Lies of P','2023-01-01','Inspired by the familiar story of Pinocchio, Lies of P is an action souls-like game set in a dark Belle Époque world. Guide Pinocchio on his unrelenting journey to become human.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co6lxr.jpg','game',NULL,8,8.5754,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-26 15:41:51',NULL,'148241',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/lies-of-p',NULL,'Round8 Studio','Lies of P',38,NULL,NULL),(1572,'Petey Wheatstraw','1977-11-01','Petey Wheatstraw (Rudy Ray Moore) is a candidate to become the devil\'s son-in-law. The storyline is a scaffolding on which Rudy Ray Moore\'s standup humor can be unfolded. Beginning life as the afterbirth to a watermelon, the young Wheatstraw becomes a martial artist, but is unable to best the evil comedy team of Leroy and Skillet, who also indulge in wholesale murder. Satan restores the comedians\' victims to life, and charges Petey with the task of marrying his clock-stoppingly ugly daughter to give him a grandchild. When Petey attempts to default on the deal, he is pursued by the devil\'s henchmen.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bQFFMMMupaCAdWcgnBjVVlbK5wq.jpg','movie',NULL,5,5.4,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-27 17:49:50','2025-01-14 06:57:45','34792',99,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0078078','Cliff Roquemore','Comedian Intl Enterprise Productions (C.I.E.)','Petey Wheatstraw',23,NULL,NULL),(1573,'Transformers One','2024-09-11','The untold origin story of Optimus Prime and Megatron, better known as sworn enemies, but once were friends bonded like brothers who changed the fate of Cybertron forever.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qrwI2T844nrBUv3eDwQZRDdgSFs.jpg','movie',NULL,7,8.088,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-30 21:42:09','2024-10-30 21:49:26','698687',104,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt8864596','Steven Spielberg','Paramount Animation','Transformers One',21,NULL,NULL),(1574,'The Big Catch: Tacklebox','2024-01-01','Crack open the Tacklebox to show off your platforming prowess and fishing skills in this free prologue to The Big Catch.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co8c6m.jpg','game',NULL,8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-30 23:41:12',NULL,'305056',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/the-big-catch-tacklebox',NULL,'Filet Group','The Big Catch: Tacklebox',NULL,NULL,3),(1575,'The Finals','2023-01-01','Join The Finals, the world-famous, free-to-play, combat-centered game show! Fight alongside your teammates in virtual arenas that you can alter, exploit, and even destroy. Build your own playstyle in this first-person shooter to win escalating tournaments and lasting fame. Can you reach The Finals?','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co8uzk.jpg','game',NULL,7,7.87834,NULL,NULL,'2024-10-30 23:41:54',NULL,'214417',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/the-finals',NULL,'Embark Studios','The Finals',37,NULL,NULL),(1576,'Day of the Dead','1985-07-03','A small group 