','1999-11-20','What is Hell for others is home for us. This is the story of Vera, Elsa, a Man, and the great love that united them. They started out growing up together but they didn\'t get very far. Leaving behind a desolate world, full of traps, they will begin a hallucinogenic journey of tenderness and violence. The story of three lovers who in a devious and gruesome manner try to destroy each other, to gain a solitary entrance to Hell.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xGGnJ81Nx8KTfQRoPzQVjlHkyAr.jpg','movie',NULL,2,6.4,NULL,NULL,'2025-01-02 06:52:27','2025-01-02 08:04:44','133523',108,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0244199','Nikos Nikolaidis','Greek Film Centre','See You in Hell, My Darling',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1625,'Phantom of the Paradise','1974-10-31','Fledgling singer-songwriter Winslow Leach finds himself double-crossed by the nefarious music producer Swan, who steals both his music and the girl Winslow wants to sing it, Phoenix, for the grand opening of his new rock palace, the Paradise. After Swan has Winslow sent to prison for trespassing, Winslow endures a freak accident that leaves him disfigured and seeking revenge.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bhM8O8yreuvbncLDP526SsBgY3B.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.5,NULL,NULL,'2024-12-31 06:53:05','2025-01-02 07:23:07','27327',92,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0071994','Michael J. Dmytryk','Harbor Productions','Phantom of the Paradise',21,NULL,NULL),(1626,'REAL','1999-01-01','Nomiya Tomomi, a high school drop-out who wants to devote his life to helping Natsumi, a girl he sentenced to a life of immobility after a tragic bike ride he invited her on, tries to change his life around, from a trouble making delinquent into a reliable man. The problem is, both Natsumi and her sister dont seem to care at all for Nomiya, rightfuly blaming him for the accident. Plus, the only notable talent Nomiya posseses is the talent for basketball. Everything changes for him when he meets up with Togawa Kiyoharu, a wheelchair basketball player.\n\n---\n- **Won the Japan Media Arts Festival Excellence Prize for Manga in 2001**','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/62b74aa6-24df-4b91-b76d-39e7ab3c3ca5/3ee77d37-69cb-4bca-b77b-3db34cffddeb.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,9,9.35509,NULL,NULL,'2025-01-02 07:35:25',NULL,'62b74aa6-24df-4b91-b76d-39e7ab3c3ca5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/62b74aa6-24df-4b91-b76d-39e7ab3c3ca5','Inoue Takehiko',NULL,'REAL',31,NULL,NULL),(1627,'The Guy She Was Interested in Wasn\'t a Guy at All','2022-01-01','Fashionable and upbeat high schooler Aya falls head over heels for an employee at a local CD shop. He’s got an air of mystery about him, always dressed well, and has impeccable taste in music. Little does she know — this supposedly male employee is actually her female classmate Mitsuki!\n\nMitsuki generally keeps to herself, but since her seat is right next to Aya’s, she can\'t help but be extremely aware of the other’s crush. Revealing the truth is out of the question — but perhaps getting closer to Aya wouldn’t be so bad...\n\n***Overwhelming winner in the Web category of the 2023 Tsugimanga Awards (by Kadokawa).***','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/9d3d3403-1a87-4737-9803-bc3d99db1424/a4c67b90-2f91-43ea-ad1f-c275c4509cde.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,7,9.47753,NULL,NULL,'2025-01-02 07:37:35',NULL,'9d3d3403-1a87-4737-9803-bc3d99db1424',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/9d3d3403-1a87-4737-9803-bc3d99db1424','Arai Sumiko',NULL,'The Guy She Was Interested in Wasn\'t a Guy at All',31,NULL,NULL),(1628,'The Exorcism','2024-05-30','A troubled actor begins to unravel while shooting a supernatural horror film, leading his estranged daughter to wonder if he\'s slipping back into his past addictions or if there\'s something more sinister at play.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ar2h87jlTfMlrDZefR3VFz1SfgH.jpg','movie',NULL,1,5.051,NULL,NULL,'2025-01-05 06:36:55','2025-01-05 06:39:12','646683',96,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt11240348',NU