he Killing Joke: The Deluxe Edition','2008-01-01','<p>Unique content and indicia.</p>','https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/10/100239/2850046-hc_batman__the_killing_joke_v1988__1___the_killing_joke__1988_6____page_1.jpg','comic',NULL,6,0,NULL,NULL,'2025-05-29 03:09:12',NULL,'56750',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/batman-the-killing-joke-the-deluxe-edition/4050-56750/','DC Comics',NULL,'Batman: The Killing Joke: The Deluxe Edition',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1704,'Little Witch Academia','2017-01-09','When she was a little girl, Atsuko \"Akko\" Kagari saw a magic show performed by a witch named Shiny Chariot.  From that day on she wanted to be just like her.  Enrolling at Luna Nova Magical Academy and having no magical background, can she become a witch like her idol Shiny Chariot?','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/93Lz0LwbScZ5bmuqoIngLv1LKNb.jpg','tv',NULL,6,7.9,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-02 17:25:02','2025-11-12 00:31:53','69293',NULL,25,1,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6352180',NULL,'TRIGGER','Little Witch Academia',26,NULL,NULL),(1705,'Skyscraper','1996-02-29','A helicopter charter turns deadly when the pilot finds that she is on a building held by terrorists. It is up to her and her husband to save the hostages.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Aq798PMmdvs3QetV8nQK6ecVx5r.jpg','movie',NULL,2,4.189,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-11 23:26:42',NULL,'42911',96,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0114467','Alexander H. Gayner','PM Entertainment Group','Skyscraper',23,NULL,NULL),(1706,'Brain Damage','1988-04-15','Brian comes under the addictive spell of a parasite with the ability to induce euphoric hallucinations in its hosts.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1fPW761HkrYAZ8c9OdCnOM9LbY4.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.7,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-15 03:59:50','2025-11-07 18:26:24','27814',86,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0094793','Greg Lamberson','Palisades Partners','Brain Damage',23,NULL,2),(1707,'Beavis and Butt-Head Do America','1996-12-20','Slacker duo Beavis and Butt-Head wake to discover their TV has been stolen. Their search for a new one takes them on a clueless adventure across America, during which they manage to accidentally become America\'s most wanted.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vqdgQiRCSzgpFXLlbxbybfkleBM.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.634,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-17 17:45:05',NULL,'3179',81,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0115641','Mike Judge','Paramount Pictures','Beavis and Butt-Head Do America',22,NULL,NULL),(1708,'King of the Hill','1997-01-12','Set in Texas, this animated series follows the life of propane salesman Hank Hill, who lives with his overly confident substitute Spanish teacher wife Peggy, wannabe comedian son Bobby, and naive niece Luanne. Hank has conservative views about God, family, and country, but his values and ethics are often challenged by the situations he, his family, and his beer-drinking neighbors/buddies find themselves in.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3MnkwPdqQ4if7HL4rYTy6eUyq8q.jpg','tv',NULL,7,7.353,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-17 21:16:59',NULL,'2122',NULL,265,14,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0118375','Greg Daniels','20th Century Fox Television','King of the Hill',28,NULL,NULL),(1709,'Showgirls','1995-09-22','Fresh to Las Vegas with no connections, Nomi Malone takes a job as an exotic dancer. Her talents are quickly noticed by Cristal, a headlining dancer who senses an opportunity to bolster her own act. But Nomi won’t play second fiddle and soon begins her venomous path to the top, ruthlessly backstabbing anyone who gets in her way.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mPHcQLyR2WXl30X4rOGHyuuWPEr.jpg','movie',NULL,3,5.6,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-22 05:59:31',NULL,'10802',131,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0114436','Paul Verhoeven','Pathé','Showgirls',24,NULL,NULL),(1710,'The Bazaar','2025-01-01','The Bazaar is the first Hero Builder, developed by Tempo. Set in a vibrant, ever-changing galactic marketplace, players assume a role from a roster of unique heroes, trading and upgrading otherworldly items & skills to assemble them into a plethora of combinations used to outplay and defeat opponents.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co2ugi.jpg','game',NULL,8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-24 16:50:15',NULL,'144274',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/the-bazaar',NULL,'Tempo Games','The Bazaar',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1711,'Mr. Ice Cream Man','1996-04-03','Children are going missing in a suburban town. There\'s a creepy guy driving an ice cream truck. Related?','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pOLOaTpcixHFBxwCmX7i9lbQo3I.jpg','movie',NULL,2,3,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-28 21:39:47',NULL,'180168',65,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0323307',NULL,NULL,'Mr. Ice Cream Man',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1712,'Who Killed Captain Alex?','2010-03-01','Recognized as Uganda’s first action film, Who Killed Captain Alex? is about the aftermath of a police raid in Kampala in which a police captain is killed.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dtPhx27ckbI2VgyeHgGPCB04ftt.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.586,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-28 21:40:48','2025-06-28 21:41:24','316776',68,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1813757','Nabwana IGG','Ramon Film Productions','Who Killed Captain Alex?',23,NULL,NULL),(1713,'Killer Workout','1987-04-16','Two years ago, a young woman named Valerie was burned after entering a tanning salon. Now, Rhonda runs a local gym where all of a sudden, people are being murdered.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tBCMvnyddaRl79lM5MrazZlPT3R.jpg','movie',NULL,2,4.613,NULL,NULL,'2025-06-30 00:31:02',NULL,'5752',84,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0091339','Susan Bierbaum','Shapiro Entertainment','Killer Workout',23,NULL,NULL),(1714,'No No Sleep','2015-04-21','In 2015, Tsai Ming-Liang was once again invited by the Hong Kong International Film Festival to make the opening short film. This time, he selected Shibuya station in Tokyo as his main filming location and invited the famous Japanese actor Masanobu Ando to appear alongside Lee Kang-Sheng. They sleep separately at a capsule hotel and cleanse themselves at a public bath. Their fatigued bodies yearn for sleep but restless minds keep them for falling asleep. \"No No Sleep\" won the Best Director Award at the Taipei Film Festival.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oXdRSO4GgBigaoHeKOk1ikkPh0G.jpg','movie',NULL,7,6.3,NULL,NULL,'2025-07-01 06:50:03','2025-07-02 16:34:54','340448',34,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4629630','Tsai Ming-liang','Hong Kong International Film Festival Society','No No Sleep',NULL,NULL,3),(1715,'Cairn','2025-01-01','Reach a summit never climbed before in this survival-climber from the creators of Furi and Haven. Climb anywhere and plan your route carefully, managing pitons and resources to survive the unforgiving Mount Kami. Discover what Aava is willing to sacrifice to achieve the ascent of a lifetime.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co9x26.jpg','game',NULL,5,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-07-01 23:07:23',NULL,'305017',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/cairn--3',NULL,'The Game Bakers','Cairn',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1716,'Kakegurui - Compulsive Gambler','2014-01-01','Hyakkaou Private Academy. An institution for the privileged with a very peculiar curriculum. You see, when you\'re the sons and daughters of the wealthiest of the wealthy, it\'s not athletic prowess or book smarts that keep you ahead. It\'s reading your opponent, the art of the deal. What better way to hone those skills than with a rigorous curriculum of gambling? At Hyakkaou Private Academy, the winners live like kings, and the losers are put through the wringer. But when Yumeko Jabami enrolls, she\'s gonna teach these kids what a high roller really looks like!\n\nPlaced 3rd in the 2nd Next Manga Awards (2016).\n___\n**Official English Volumes:** [Yen Press](https://yenpress.com/series/kakegurui-compulsive-gambler)\n\n**Original Concept:** [Dominium ~The Gambling Legend Of Extremely Colorful Girls~](http://ushimilk.web.fc2.com/index.html)','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/0951feea-ba41-4ad0-9cb0-edadc77eae73/2b06185b-c8cc-42af-8717-46c97d4d4e4a.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,7,8.13318,NULL,NULL,'2025-07-02 23:08:42',NULL,'0951feea-ba41-4ad0-9cb0-edadc77eae73',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/0951feea-ba41-4ad0-9cb0-edadc77eae73','Kawamoto Homura',NULL,'Kakegurui - Compulsive Gambler',32,NULL,NULL),(1717,'Robots','2005-03-10','Rodney Copperbottom is a young robot inventor who dreams of making the world a better place, until the evil Ratchet takes over Bigweld Industries. Now, Rodney\'s dreams – and those of his friends – are in danger of becoming obsolete.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fnKCh67l2DDG9NxxIlk9IpsXQ99.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.47,NULL,NULL,'2025-07-07 00:45:09','2025-07-07 00:45:46','9928',90,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0358082','Enrico Casarosa','Blue Sky Studios','Robots',21,NULL,NULL),(1718,'Vibrations','1996-07-02','A musician who lost his hands falls for a woman whose technologically adept friends help him make a comeback.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/y36olpgBRBmT0DaIfPD291q3jVe.jpg','movie',NULL,3,3.45,NULL,NULL,'2025-07-12 07:17:47',NULL,'106258',104,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0114845','Michael Slovis','Dimension Films','Vibrations',23,NULL,NULL),(1719,'The Mummy Theme Park','2000-01-01','Sheik El Sahid has built a theme park at the underground holy City of the Dead in Egypt that an earthquake has revealed. Two American publicists are brought over to make it a success, to advertise its fantastic mechanised speaking mummies. The place soon appears to be cursed especially when the ancient mummies begin breaking free and wreaking havoc.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iwW1Z9a97tLAanON6z94gTyzWmB.jpg','movie',NULL,2,4.5,NULL,NULL,'2025-07-12 07:39:26',NULL,'56721',87,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0391355',NULL,'Production Film 82','The Mummy Theme Park',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1720,'Armored Core VI: Fires of Rubicon','2023-01-01','By combining FromSoftware’s longstanding expertise in mech games and their signature robust gameplay, Armored Core VI: Fires of Rubicon will be a new action experience.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co6ffo.jpg','game',NULL,5,8.34074,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-06 04:45:18','2025-08-06 04:46:21','228542',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/armored-core-vi-fires-of-rubicon',NULL,'FromSoftware','Armored Core VI: Fires of Rubicon',37,NULL,2),(1721,'Viewfinder','2023-01-01','Viewfinder is a puzzle game where you can reshape the world around you by taking photos with an instant camera.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co6m9m.jpg','game',NULL,6,8.37184,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-06 04:45:50',NULL,'142549',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/viewfinder',NULL,'Sad Owl Studios','Viewfinder',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1722,'Blue Prince','2025-01-01','Welcome to Mt. Holly, where every dawn unveils a new mystery. Navigate through shifting corridors and ever-changing chambers in this genre-defying strategy puzzle adventure. But will the unpredictable path you create lead you to the rumored Room 46?','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co9mzd.jpg','game',NULL,7,8.92977,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-06 04:46:01',NULL,'149657',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/blue-prince',NULL,'Dogubomb','Blue Prince',35,NULL,NULL),(1723,'The King is Watching','2025-01-01','In this casual strategy game, you\'ll be able to defend your kingdom from enemy invaders and gather various resources.','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co7muc.jpg','game',NULL,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-06 04:47:32',NULL,'282826',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/the-king-is-watching',NULL,'Hypnohead','The King is Watching',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1724,'Keep on Mining!','2025-01-01','Keep on Mining! is a short incremental mining game. Mine rocks, gather material, find artifact, craft pickaxes and spend your materials on permanent upgrades inside the big skill tree!','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/coa7if.jpg','game',NULL,7,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-06 09:05:04',NULL,'349928',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/keep-on-mining',NULL,NULL,'Keep on Mining!',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1725,'Wizard So So: Fun Magical Adventure','2008-11-11','Two stories: When Kitty the Cat struggles to rid Farmer Fred\'s barn of the three mean-spirited rat bullies that have been stealing food and causing trouble, Wizard So So steps in to lend the feline a magical helping hand. In the second story of this charming animated adventure, Wizard So So comes to the aid of his friend the Dragonfly, who dreams of turning into an actually flying dragon..','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xaQh1id6vXCIhjnc4iKTKtmpyXN.jpg','movie',NULL,2,2,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-18 05:04:49',NULL,'559572',58,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt11354142','Rina Wayanti','Celebrity Video','Wizard So So: Fun Magical Adventure',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1726,'Killer Tongue','1996-11-15','A bank robber seeks refuge in a desert gas station run by nuns, awaiting her boyfriend\'s release. An alien meteorite transforms her into a flesh-craving monster with a monstrous tongue, while her poodles become drag queens.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mYFmBlGOnpkn2ODcyBYP5Q7RI7m.jpg','movie',NULL,6,5.486,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-18 05:05:18','2025-08-18 05:06:43','36271',98,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0116770','Alberto Sciamma','Spice Factory','Killer Tongue',23,NULL,NULL),(1727,'Baby\'s Day Out','1994-07-01','Baby Bink couldn\'t ask for more: he has adoring (if somewhat sickly-sweet) parents, lives in a huge mansion, and he\'s just about to appear in the social pages of the paper. Unfortunately, not everyone in the world is as nice as Baby Bink\'s parents—especially the three enterprising kidnappers who pretend to be photographers from the newspaper. Successfully kidnapping Baby Bink, they have a harder time keeping hold of the rascal, who not only keeps one step ahead of them, but seems to be more than a little bit smarter than the three bumbling criminals.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lb4FtRVilfF9ZL8rlcuAPURUhzG.jpg','movie',NULL,1,6.387,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-18 05:05:50','2025-08-18 05:07:23','11212',99,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0109190','Patrick Read Johnson','20th Century Fox','Baby\'s Day Out',21,NULL,NULL),(1728,'Yomi no Tsugai','2021-01-01','The manga centers on Yuru, a boy who lives in a remote mountain village, spending his time hunting birds and being one with nature. But one day, Yuru\'s younger twin sister Asa is called to serve in the jail at the heart of the village, her duty also confining her there. Yuru slowly unravels the unnatural mystery hidden beneath his quiet village.\n___\n**Official English Volumes:** [Square Enix Manga & Books](https://squareenixmangaandbooks.square-enix-games.com/en-us/series/daemons-of-the-shadow-realm)\n**Official Indonesian Volumes:** [Elex Media Komputindo](https://elexmedia.id/produk/judul/yomi%20no%20tsugai%20-%20pair%20of%20the%20underworld)','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/b340d77a-6bfe-4f33-8352-4d305ecf264c/2f592bd6-b1c6-4b30-a457-cbcd75f1edaf.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,7,8.72669,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-20 20:15:30',NULL,'b340d77a-6bfe-4f33-8352-4d305ecf264c',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/b340d77a-6bfe-4f33-8352-4d305ecf264c','Arakawa Hiromu',NULL,'Yomi no Tsugai',31,NULL,NULL),(1729,'High School Musical','2006-01-20','A popular high school athlete and an academically gifted girl get roles in the school musical and develop a friendship that threatens East High\'s social order.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bg1eLo2OjySRYKaTO89ZDsqUcJ4.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.548,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-15 04:53:22',NULL,'10947',98,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0475293','Kenny Ortega','Salty Pictures','High School Musical',20,NULL,NULL),(1730,'High School Musical 2','2007-08-17','The East High Wildcats are gearing up for big fun as they land the coolest summer jobs imaginable. Troy, Gabriella, Chad, and Taylor have scored sweet gigs at the Lava Springs Country Club owned by Sharpay and Ryan\'s family. Sharpay\'s first rule of business: Get Troy. As Troy experiences a life of privilege he\'s never known, will he give up the Wildcats and Gabriella to rise to the top?','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/la2kiVWDm2vuB4APZDgCCmuBh4K.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.508,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-15 04:53:36',NULL,'13649',111,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0810900','Kenny Ortega','First Street Films','High School Musical 2',20,NULL,NULL),(1731,'LEGO Star Wars: Rebuild the Galaxy','2024-09-13','The entire Star Wars galaxy gets completely mixed up when an ordinary nerf-herder, Sig Greebling, unearths a powerful artifact from a hidden Jedi temple. He finds himself thrust into adventure in a new, wondrously wild and twisted version of the galaxy where good guys are bad, bad guys are good, and the fate of all depends on Sig becoming the hero who can put all the pieces back together.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5dKXqeeRWymBysWM8VyLEhVwyLh.jpg','tv',NULL,6,7.2,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-19 18:20:40','2025-11-12 00:30:47','253760',NULL,4,1,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt32306451','Dan Hernandez','Lucasfilm Ltd.','LEGO Star Wars: Rebuild the Galaxy',26,NULL,NULL),(1732,'Raggedy Ann & Andy: A Musical Adventure!','1977-04-01','Raggedy Ann and Andy, along with other toys, reside in the nursery of a little girl named Marcella. During Marcella\'s seventh birthday, Babette, from France, is introduced as the new doll from a large package. Meanwhile, the lecherous Captain Contagious kidnaps Babette in his pirate ship and escapes from the nursery. Ann and Andy must explore and find Babette in the Deep Deep Woods to save her.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2zjHn9qzEfPsXg0PDZAJI4CoEGF.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.8,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-20 08:03:44','2025-09-22 18:35:56','36748',85,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0076593','Richard Williams','ITT Inc.','Raggedy Ann & Andy: A Musical Adventure!',20,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AloMFCbn4IQ&pp=ygUUcmFnZ2VkeSBhbm4gYW5kIGFuZHk%3D',2),(1733,'Over the Garden Wall','2014-11-03','Two brothers, Wirt and Greg, find themselves lost in the Unknown; a strange forest adrift in time. With the help of a wise old Woodsman and a foul-tempered bluebird named Beatrice, Wirt and Greg must travel across this strange land, in hope of finding their way home. Join them as they encounter surprises and obstacles on their journey through the wood.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m3lU8n7WxzMecxKZcqhq5y5ESy.jpg','tv',NULL,7,8.6,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-30 17:40:52','2025-09-30 17:43:01','61617',NULL,10,1,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3718778','Patrick McHale','Cartoon Network Studios','Over the Garden Wall',28,NULL,NULL),(1734,'Don\'t Hug Me I\'m Scared','2022-09-30','Join Red Guy, Yellow Guy and Duck as they learn everything there is to know with the help of some friendly talking objects, in this comedy-horror puppet show based off the popular YouTube web series.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tbVObZCnCOjaC06F08nhuXygti0.jpg','tv',NULL,7,8.5,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-02 22:20:01',NULL,'206013',NULL,6,1,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt14932528','Becky Sloan','Blink Industries','Don\'t Hug Me I\'m Scared',30,NULL,2),(1735,'The Devils','1971-07-16','In 1634 France, Urbain Grandier is a priest whose unorthodox views on sex and religion influence a passionate following of nuns, including the sexually obsessed Sister Jeanne. When power-hungry Cardinal Richelieu realizes he must eliminate Grandier to gain control of France, he portrays Grandier as a satanist and spearheads a public outcry to destroy the once-loved priest\'s reputation.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ltuRwbbShGj7205FhJBKpmDzGa4.jpg','movie',NULL,8,7.5,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-03 05:30:10',NULL,'31767',114,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0066993','Ken Russell','Russo Productions','The Devils',23,NULL,NULL),(1736,'Sword of the Sea','2025-01-01','Sword of the Sea is an action-adventure game developed