r horizons!','https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/co8bud.jpg','game',NULL,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-03 21:37:39',NULL,'305171',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.igdb.com/games/star-birds',NULL,'Toukana Interactive','Star Birds',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1740,'Love on a Leash','2011-07-21','A dog who strives to become a man seeks a woman who will love him enough for the transformation to take place.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lKMaQ0kbaPGjJA5OzZP13z8sbw9.jpg','movie',NULL,5,6.447,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-05 16:26:31','2025-10-05 20:01:28','307124',86,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2185022','Danielle Snowdon','Fenix Pictures','Love on a Leash',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1741,'Sweet Trash','1970-06-15','An alcoholic longshoreman, deep in debt to the mob, is forced into an increasingly debauched nightmare as he tries to avoid the thugs out to get him. Along the way, he meets local oddballs, violent criminals, and lusty women. With a mysterious computer controlling everyone’s actions this grimy artistic film with almost science fiction-esque fear of future mind control was made well before it’s time.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mkIWLYFAqg9kTdmEXcpGOjOclCD.jpg','movie',NULL,3,4.8,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-05 16:28:06',NULL,'353087',79,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0066426','John Hayes',NULL,'Sweet Trash',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1742,'Human Highway','1982-09-10','The new owner of a roadside diner stuck in a town built around an always leaking nuclear power plant plans to torch the place to collect insurance. However, an assortment of bizarre characters and weird events (such as spaceships flying around) gets in his way.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ji18nHQWxiyoq3r7HHyohdJFOCt.jpg','movie',NULL,3,5,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-05 16:28:35',NULL,'70011',88,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0084099',NULL,'Shakey Pictures','Human Highway',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1743,'Blood for Dracula','1974-08-13','Deathly ill Count Dracula and his slimy underling, Anton, travel to Italy in search