om/title/tt7655524',NULL,'MC2 Productions','Playing Hard',20,NULL,NULL),(1747,'In the Mouth of Madness','1995-02-03','An insurance investigator visits a small town while looking into the disappearance of a popular horror novelist. He soon finds that the impact of the author’s books is far more than inspirational.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/acpkk92oV33Q47mf7kTKlNwt4op.jpg','movie',NULL,5,7.21,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-08 18:11:51',NULL,'2654',95,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0113409','John Carpenter','New Line Cinema','In the Mouth of Madness',23,NULL,NULL),(1748,'Requiem for a Vampire','2006-04-22','An incestuous and industrious pair of modern-day vampires finds their clever manner of acquiring sustenance threatened by a nosy New Jersey health inspector and a determined investigative reporter in director John Orrichio\'s sexualized tale of life among the undead. The LeGaults know well that to stalk the streets for prey is to leave themselves open to exposure. Instead of seeking out blood the old-fashioned way, the LeGaults opt to open a blood donation center that will provide them with the nourishment they need to survive without the risks that go along with using their fangs. A New Jersey health inspector named Jerry is on to them, though, and along with a little help from intrepid reporter Phyllis, he soon prepares to rip the lid off of the LeGault\'s bizarre scam. When a chance encounter with two students of the occult reveals the true motivation behind the LeGaults\' philanthropic front...','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/AaQzSANVXD5tBjEcder0bB0DqTa.jpg','movie',NULL,1,5.1,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-08 18:13:28',NULL,'147151',94,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0824768','Karl Petry','Orrichio Films','Requiem for a Vampire',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1749,'The Witching','1993-01-01','A family finds that the refrigerator in their kitchen is a gateway to Hell, and they must battle a witch.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eX1NPDPEvtnA0Z7lk5R1DxapEvO.jpg','movie',N