.com/title/tt14205554','Chris Appelhans','Sony Pictures Animation','KPop Demon Hunters',21,NULL,NULL),(1797,'Breaking the Waves','1996-07-05','In a small, conservative Scottish village, an oilman is paralyzed in an accident. His wife, who prayed for his return, feels guilty; even more, when he urges her to have sex with another.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/w9Ff5yhAnw11VYHbOatI2Uf6cQI.jpg','movie',NULL,6,7.5,NULL,NULL,'2026-01-27 22:29:21','2026-01-29 23:07:38','145',159,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0115751','Lars von Trier','Zentropa Entertainments','Breaking the Waves',23,NULL,3),(1798,'WHY WE FIGHT BACK // Season 2026 Cinematic Kickoff Trailer - VALORANT','2026-01-10',NULL,'https://img.youtube.com/vi/AnGdzz-XWcE/maxresdefault.jpg','youtube',NULL,8,9.84813,NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 00:38:08',NULL,'AnGdzz-XWcE',4,NULL,NULL,NULL,'VALORANT',NULL,'WHY WE FIGHT BACK // Season 2026 Cinematic Kickoff Trailer - VALORANT',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AnGdzz-XWcE',NULL),(1799,'What\'s in a Name','2012-04-25','Vincent, a wealthy real estate agent, is invited to dinner by his sister Elizabeth and her husband Peter, both professors in Paris. Claude, a childhood friend and trombonist in a symphony orchestra, is also present. Vincent brings news from the prenatal examination of his and his wife Anna\'s unborn son.  The name chosen by the soon-to-be parents strongly offends the others for many reasons. The dispute between the guests quickly escalates and before long the resurgence of old grudges and hidden secrets is unavoidable...','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5xKkDkv506CiSp99SxmHLsnaoFs.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.321,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-08 07:22:12',NULL,'112198',109,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2179121',NULL,'Chapter 2','What\'s in a Name',20,NULL,2),(1800,'The Fisher King','1991-09-20','Two troubled men face their terrible destinies and events of their past as they join together on a mission to find the Holy Grail and thus to save themselves.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hwIYw22HmAUMobV4zsX69MgfVUz.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.31,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-10 05:47:32',NULL,'177',138,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0101889','Terry Gilliam','TriStar Pictures','The Fisher King',23,NULL,NULL),(1801,'Orb: On the Movements of the Earth','2020-01-01','The setting is 15th century Poland. It was a time when heretical ideas lead those to who possessed such a mindset to being burned at the stake for their beliefs. Rafal, a child prodigy, is expected to major in theology, the most important subject at the time, at the university. One day, however, he comes across a mysterious man, and is now studying a possible “truth” in the midst of heretical thought!\n\n**Awards:**\n- Won the 26th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Awards Manga Grand Prize (2022).\n- Won the 54th Seiun Award in the Comics Division (2023).\n- Won #1 in BookLive\'s Readers\' Choice Top 100 Truely Interesting Manga 2025.','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/183b5c1e-5bfd-4f7f-9b21-3ac88c584987/43019efd-cb1a-443f-9fda-f61f7cd54d89.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,7,9.13791,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-16 23:53:39',NULL,'183b5c1e-5bfd-4f7f-9b21-3ac88c584987',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://mangadex.org/title/183b5c1e-5bfd-4f7f-9b21-3ac88c584987','Uoto',NULL,NULL,31,NULL,NULL),(1802,'The Last Republican','2024-09-05','A fan of Hot Tub Time Machine, Republican Congressman Adam Kinzinger invites the left-wing Hollywood director Steve Pink to follow his efforts to hold Donald Trump accountable for the January 6 insurrection.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vch24Xc8c4M2Ku81wMCKAyiea8N.jpg','movie',NULL,7,6.9,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-07 00:05:21',NULL,'1326904',88,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt33084850','Steve Pink',NULL,'The Last Republican',22,NULL,NULL),(1803,'Evil Dead II','1987-03-13','Ash Williams and his girlfriend Linda find a log cabin in the woods with a voice recording from an archeologist who had recorded himself reciting ancient chants from \"The Book of the Dead.\" As they play the recording an evil power is unleashed taking over Linda\'s body.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4zqCKJVHUolGs6C5AZwAZqLWixW.jpg','movie',NULL,7,7.543,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-08 09:17:53','2026-03-08 09:19:27','765',84,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0092991','Sam Raimi','Rosebud Releasing Corporation','Evil Dead II',23,NULL,NULL),(1804,'Cool World','1992-07-10','While incarcerated for murder, cartoonist Jack Deebs found escape by creating Cool World, a series featuring a voluptuous femme fatale named Holli Would. But the artist becomes a prisoner of his own fantasies when Holli transports Jack into Cool World with a scheme to seduce him and bring herself to life. Hard-boiled detective Frank Harris – the only other human in Cool World – cautions Jack with the law: Noids (humans) don\'t have sex with doodles (cartoons). However, flesh proves weaker than ink as Holli takes human form in Las Vegas, staring in a trans-universal chase that threatens the destruction of both worlds.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mqzRUHNtFwmgJCmSnvq3JnX0xgZ.jpg','movie',NULL,7,5.632,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-08 09:18:15','2026-03-08 09:26:04','14239',102,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0104009','Ralph Bakshi','Paramount Pictures','Cool World',22,NULL,NULL),(1805,'Jackie','2016-12-02','An account of the days of First Lady, Jacqueline Kennedy, in the immediate aftermath of John F. Kennedy\'s assassination in 1963.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nF9N33PfhizMEzbfxHoxXBo2vx9.jpg','movie',NULL,6,6.5,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-14 06:08:34',NULL,'376866',100,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1619029','Pablo Larraín','LD Entertainment','Jackie',23,NULL,NULL),(1806,'We\'re Back! A Dinosaur\'s Story','1993-11-24','Captain New Eyes travels back in time and feeds dinosaurs his Brain Grain cereal, which makes them intelligent and non-violent. They agree to go to the \"Middle Future\" in order to grant the wishes of children in New York City. They are to meet Dr. Bleeb of the Museum of Natural History, but get sidetracked with their new children friends and run into the Captain\'s evil brother, Professor Screweyes.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iyFmhYlioe3PDZjSKWtcIhu5R02.jpg','movie',NULL,2,6.088,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-16 16:48:58','2026-03-16 16:51:15','18890',71,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0108526','Phil Nibbelink','Amblin Entertainment','We\'re Back! A Dinosaur\'s Story',20,NULL,NULL),(1807,'Sinners','2025-04-16','Trying to leave their troubled lives behind, twin brothers return to their hometown to start again, only to discover that an even greater evil is waiting to welcome them back.','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cuM1rGXxTd28KEQXBG683ODtWPY.jpg','movie',NULL,3,7.472,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-17 06:32:48','2026-03-17 17:55:29','1233413',138,NULL,NULL,'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt31193180','Ryan Coogler','Warner Bros. Pictures','Sinners',23,NULL,NULL),(1808,'The Bugle Call: Song of War','2022-01-01','In Arboral Year 1294, the world is dominated by nine massive towers known as the Spires, remnants of an ancient civilization. Filled with lost secrets and powerful knowledge, nations struggle to possess them. Luca is a bugler in a mercenary company who wants nothing more than to leave the battlefield behind and become a true musician, a maestro. But marked as one of the enigmatic Branch-hexed, and gifted with the strange ability to see the sound of his instrument, Luca finds himself drawn reluctantly into a war of epic proportions!\n\nLeft for dead after a battle, Luca is saved by the mysterious Pontiff and learns he is not the only person with unusual powers. The Pontiff has formed a special team of Branch-hexed individuals he plans to use to help him defeat rival empires, and Luca learns that his powers, rather than being an escape from the battlefield, now force him to be a muse of massacre.','https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/f7b62193-bdfb-4953-a6c6-0bd1b9a872f9/9e564985-2acf-40c2-8586-462d465c1ed6.jpg.512.jpg','manga',NULL,8,9.39408,